(85, 'An evidence-driven framework for trustworthiness evaluation of software based on rules', 'uploadFile/bb759c4e-5b7e-48e2-b05c-1e29295a4f12.mht', 'SCI全文检索期刊，EI已检索', 99, 95, 49, '2012-11-30 15:37:40', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Chinese Journal of Electronics', '2012-10', 'Trusted software, Trustworthiness evaluation, Evidence-driven, Rules', 'Through the analysis and research on existing trusted software evaluation technology, an evidencedriven framework for trustworthiness evaluation of software based on rules is put forward, rules are used as expression method of trustworthiness evaluation logic, and evidence is used to drive the operation of trustworthiness evaluation process, trustworthiness evidence collection and processing logic as well as mapping method of trustworthiness levels have been encapsulated in rules, and the selection, instantiation, collection, format definition and measurement of trustworthiness evidence are carried out under the guidance of the rules, and the mapping of trustworthiness levels and the analysis of trustworthiness bottleneck are done based on the measured evidence instances, this framework has provided an application implementation scheme for software trustworthiness evaluation.', 'Through the analysis and research on existing trusted software evaluation technology, an evidencedriven framework for trustworthiness evaluation of software based on rules is put forward, rules are used as expression method of trustworthiness evaluation logic, and evidence is used to drive the operation of trustworthiness evaluation process, trustworthiness evidence collection and processing logic as well as mapping method of trustworthiness levels have been encapsulated in rules, and the selection, instantiation, collection, format definition and measurement of trustworthiness evidence are carried out under the guidance of the rules, and the mapping of trustworthiness levels and the analysis of trustworthiness bottleneck are done based on the measured evidence instances, this framework has provided an application implementation scheme for software trustworthiness evaluation.', '20124615657810', 0.147, 0, '21', '4', '589-593', NULL, '', 2, 'Wang Xiaoyan, Liu Shufen, Bao Tie', 't', '62', 'SCI全文检索期刊，EI已检索'),
(86, '一种用于评价语义Web服务质量的多属性关系建模方法', 'uploadFile/004cb3f2-447f-40fd-aa31-3f281adfb030.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5075b08fb94prod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 99, 99, 45, '2012-11-30 15:48:03', '2012-12-07', '1', '电子学报', '2012-08', '语义Web 服务，服务质量评价，多属性关系', '针对语义Web服务的处理能力空闲、服务请求过载和功能失效的服务质量评价问题,提出一种用于评价语义Web服务质量的多属性关系建模方法,从技术层面和社会层面上选取一组服务质量评价指标并定义其属性计算模型,分析出各评价指标之间的属性关系并证明其一致性,利用现有样本进行实验验证并给出性能分析. 更多还原\n', 'To the qualitative problem of capability idle, request overload and function invalidation of the semantic web service,\nwe proposed a method to model the relationships between mult-i attributes for evaluating the quality of the semantic web service.\nWe chose a set of evaluation indexes which are both on the aspects of technolo gy and society, and defined their attributes.\ncomputing models, made the analysis on potential relationships between the attributes and proved consistency, and utilized an existing\nswatch to do experiment for the capability analy sis and effect validation of this proposed method.', '20124215582350', 0, 0, '40', '8', '1591-1596', NULL, '', 1.5, '曲明，刘淑芬，包铁', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5075b08fb94prod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(87, '基于PBDM划分权限的授权代理模型', 'uploadFile/3772f49b-f01f-4ea7-8a7d-ee2281b21364.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201205038&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 99, 99, 44, '2012-11-30 15:52:35', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(理学版)', '2012-09', '授权代理，角色，权限', '在PBDM 授权代理模型的基础上，提出一种新的授权代理模型PBDM-P，将角色划分为常规角色、私有角色和临时代理角色，将权限划分为可代理权限和不可代理权限． PBDM-P通过划分角色和权限实现了用户-用户授权代理、角色-角色授权代理，从而有效解决了角色名空间爆炸和空角色等问题，保证了系统的安全访问，使授权代理更灵活．', 'The authors introduced a new delegation model based on the permission-based delegation model\n( PBDM) ． The roles are divided into three sets，which include regular roles，private roles and delegation\nroles． The permissions are divides into two sets，which include delegatable permissions and un-delegatable\npermissions． This new model supports user-to-user and role-to-role delegation， effectively avoids some\nproblems such as name space explosion and void roles，ensures the safety of access to the system，and makes\nthe delegation more flexible．', '0', 0, 0, '50', '5', '1007-1010', NULL, '', 0.25, '张秉阁，刘淑芬，韩啸', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201205038&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(88, 'A routing attack detection method for cluster wireless sensor networks', 'uploadFile/829e4e09-5283-43ae-8fa4-f3fe81ccb944.mht', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=5bcf29ba13b50eafd25M1f09prod3con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 99, 99, 41, '2012-11-30 15:59:33', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Theoretical and Applied Information Technology', '2012-08', 'Computer crime,Military applications,Network layers  -  Network routing,Network security,Target tracking ', 'Wireless sensor networks have been widely used in many applications such as military monitoring, target tracking and surveillance. Security issue is need to more concern. Routing protocol is the core technology of the network layer in wireless sensor networks. Many attackers disrupt the network with routing attack, which will do serious damage to wireless sensor networks. Consider the scare energy and limitation computation capability of sensors, traditional security detection method is not fit for wireless sensor networks. In this paper, we focus on malicious attacks on routing and detection method in wireless sensor networks. We analyze most kinds of attacks and threats on routing, and then propose a routing attack detection method for cluster wireless sensor networks.', 'Wireless sensor networks have been widely used in many applications such as military monitoring, target tracking and surveillance. Security issue is need to more concern. Routing protocol is the core technology of the network layer in wireless sensor networks. Many attackers disrupt the network with routing attack, which will do serious damage to wireless sensor networks. Consider the scare energy and limitation computation capability of sensors, traditional security detection method is not fit for wireless sensor networks. In this paper, we focus on malicious attacks on routing and detection method in wireless sensor networks. We analyze most kinds of attacks and threats on routing, and then propose a routing attack detection method for cluster wireless sensor networks.', '20124015492247', 0, 0, '42', '2', '166-170', NULL, '', 2, 'Shen Zihao, Liu Shufen', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=5bcf29ba13b50eafd25M1f09prod3con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(89, 'Security threats and security policy in wireless sensor networks', 'uploadFile/c78af24d-484b-4f32-8bca-4b4d68ccd7c6.mht', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b51a3487bM5fa8prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 99, 99, 41, '2012-11-30 16:05:26', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Advances in Information Sciences and Service Sciences', '2012-06', 'Military applications,Network security,Security systems  -  Target tracking,Wireless telecommunication systems ', 'A wireless sensor network (WSN) consists of several hundreds, or even thousands of small wireless sensors that have sensing, processing, and communication capabilities over wireless channels. As an emerging technology, WSNs are being used in a wide variety of applications such as environmental monitoring, earthquake and target tracking, military security, etc. Wireless sensor networks are usually deployed with lacking in careful surveillance in unattended and hostile environments to perform various kinds of tasks. Consequently, WSNs may encounter more and more threats and attacks. These threats and attacks will do serious damage to WSNs. At the same time, scarce resource constraints, unreliable wireless communications, uncontrolled sensing environment make it difficult to adopt traditional security techniques. In this paper, the security issue of WSNs is studied. First, WSNs communication protocol stack is introduced and thirteen types of malicious attacks are analyzed. Then, a new WSNs threat model is proposed, which enumerates the various attacks that may be launched on the WSN from different perspectives. Finally, security strategy for WSNs is discussed in detail. Through WSNs security requirements analysis, a security framework for WSNs can be established, which can effectively solve the WSNs security issue.', 'A wireless sensor network (WSN) consists of several hundreds, or even thousands of small wireless sensors that have sensing, processing, and communication capabilities over wireless channels. As an emerging technology, WSNs are being used in a wide variety of applications such as environmental monitoring, earthquake and target tracking, military security, etc. Wireless sensor networks are usually deployed with lacking in careful surveillance in unattended and hostile environments to perform various kinds of tasks. Consequently, WSNs may encounter more and more threats and attacks. These threats and attacks will do serious damage to WSNs. At the same time, scarce resource constraints, unreliable wireless communications, uncontrolled sensing environment make it difficult to adopt traditional security techniques. In this paper, the security issue of WSNs is studied. First, WSNs communication protocol stack is introduced and thirteen types of malicious attacks are analyzed. Then, a new WSNs threat model is proposed, which enumerates the various attacks that may be launched on the WSN from different perspectives. Finally, security strategy for WSNs is discussed in detail. Through WSNs security requirements analysis, a security framework for WSNs can be established, which can effectively solve the WSNs security issue.', '20122615179823', 0, 2, '4', '10', '166-173', NULL, '', 2, 'Shen Zihao, Liu Shufen', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b51a3487bM5fa8prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(90, 'A collaborative simulation monitor system of ship based on patterns', 'uploadFile/7f68c962-c9dd-41ab-a611-e60a73912698.mht', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b506692af24b6prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 99, 99, 47, '2012-11-30 16:10:35', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Proceedings of 2012 International Symposium on Information Technologies in Medicine and Education, ITME 2012', '2012-08', 'Computer simulation, Computer software reusability ,Reusability ,Structural design ', 'Computer simulation has been widely used in scientific research. But the present simulation systems are mostly designed for a specific purpose, which can only be applied in specific research experiment, so the expansibility is not good. The main purpose of pattern technology is to extend the technologies of software reuse based on Object Oriented [1]. Pattern technology can reuse not only the codes of function modules, but also the structural design of system software. In the design and implementation of the collaborative ship simulation monitor system mentioned in this paper, kinds of pattern technologies have been used. The system has not just the characteristics of high efficiency, easy to extend and maintain, but also the characteristic of high reusability. ', 'Computer simulation has been widely used in scientific research. But the present simulation systems are mostly designed for a specific purpose, which can only be applied in specific research experiment, so the expansibility is not good. The main purpose of pattern technology is to extend the technologies of software reuse based on Object Oriented [1]. Pattern technology can reuse not only the codes of function modules, but also the structural design of system software. In the design and implementation of the collaborative ship simulation monitor system mentioned in this paper, kinds of pattern technologies have been used. The system has not just the characteristics of high efficiency, easy to extend and maintain, but also the characteristic of high reusability. ', '20124315606184', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-08-03', 'Hokkaido, Japan', 0.25, 'Wu Jun, Liu Shufen', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b506692af24b6prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(91, 'A Role-based feature model componentization framework and related algorithms', 'uploadFile/29f3311c-3571-41a7-b09c-55d3b50723e3.mht', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b506692af24b6prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=4&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 99, 99, 47, '2012-11-30 16:13:46', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Proceedings of the 2012 IEEE 16th International Conference on Computer Supported Cooperative Work in Design, CSCWD 2012', '2012-05', 'Design,Interactive computer systems ', 'As a kind of requirement model, feature model represents functions of a family of products in a uniform form. To solve the chaos and entanglement problem in the process of feature model description and configuration, this paper designs a feature model componentization framework. With the help of the concept of Role and Reference Role, the framework proposes a process to analyze and decompose complex requirement specification to simple and coherent roles, and then implements Feature -Role-Component algorithms which map all features generated by requirement elicitation and analysis to different model components. In the framework and algorithms, role and reference role plays as an intermediary who decouple the feature and component, which makes convenient feature variants selection and composition and enhances the componentization level of the system. By decomposing the system functions in the early phase of software lifecycle, the framework improves the flexibility and adaptability of software artifact, which makes a stable foundation for higher quality product. ', 'As a kind of requirement model, feature model represents functions of a family of products in a uniform form. To solve the chaos and entanglement problem in the process of feature model description and configuration, this paper designs a feature model componentization framework. With the help of the concept of Role and Reference Role, the framework proposes a process to analyze and decompose complex requirement specification to simple and coherent roles, and then implements Feature -Role-Component algorithms which map all features generated by requirement elicitation and analysis to different model components. In the framework and algorithms, role and reference role plays as an intermediary who decouple the feature and component, which makes convenient feature variants selection and composition and enhances the componentization level of the system. By decomposing the system functions in the early phase of software lifecycle, the framework improves the flexibility and adaptability of software artifact, which makes a stable foundation for higher quality product. ', '20123115289404', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-05-23', 'Wuhan, China', 0.25, 'Zhang Jun, Liu Shufen', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b506692af24b6prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=4&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(92, 'Using Spatial Reasoning in CPM based Image Retrieval', 'uploadFile/e537d0b1-6883-43b4-9beb-ca2601614a7b.pdf', 'http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-25789-6_6', 243, 243, 41, '2012-12-01 05:24:05', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Lecture Notes in Electrical Engineering', '2012-01', '空间推理,图像检索', '在基于CPM的图像检索中应用空间推理', 'Traditional image retrieval methods are based on the spatial relationship regarding objects as centroids, and take the advantage of point based spatial relational models to measure the similarity of images. They can not distinguish the di-rectional or topological relationship, so it will return irrelative results. We give a new image retrieval algorithm RACPM by using spatial reasoning and common pattern method. The RACPM compares the rectangle algebra expression of the ob-jects both in the query image and the database image on the x axis and the y axis, and these two pairs are “similar” if and only if all the expressions of them are identical respectively. Compared with the original CPM, the experimental results show that the RACPM outperforms CPM, not only on the time consuming, but also provides more precise retrieval results. ', 'EI', 0, 0, '125', '1', '33-38', NULL, '', 0.25, 'Shengsheng Wang, Chuo Dong and Dayou Liu', 't', '63', 'http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-25789-6_6'),
(93, '基于作者权威值的论文价值预测算法', 'uploadFile/182f78b0-d36b-45c4-9989-818e3831bb98.pdf', '无', 232, 232, 45, '2012-12-01 05:29:50', '2012-12-07', '1', '自动化学报', '2012-10', '引用网络, 排名预测, FutureRank, PageRank', '论文引用网络是一个动态变化的网络, 不断有新的论文加入引用网络中. 传统的论文评价标准如引用次\n数、PageRank 值等\\终身评价标准" 存在排挤新结点的问题, 如何在海量论文中寻找有价值、被持续关注的论文, 成为\n人们感兴趣的问题. Sayyadi 提出了FutureRank 算法, 该算法通过预测论文未来\\一段时间" 的被引次数排名和PageRank\n值排名来达到这一目的. 但FutureRank 算法要提前计算PageRank 值, 要耗费大量运算时间. 据此, 我们尝试在不计算论文\n现有PageRank 值的条件下, 从论文的撰写者以及引用者的权威值的角度来预测论文未来的被引次数排名和PageRank 值排\n名. 实验结果表明, 我们的算法与FutureRank 相比, 不但缩短了运算时间, 而且提高了预测准确率.', 'Citation network is a dynamic network, and new papers are added to it every day. The traditional literature\nevaluation criteria like citations number and PageRank, are unfair to the new node. How to retrieve the valuable papers\nof continuous concerns has become an interesting focus. To solve this problem, Hassan Sayyadi proposed the FutureRank\nalgorithm, but it needs to calculate the PageRank value, which Spends a lot of time. Accordingly, we proposed a paper\nvalue prediction algorithm without computing the PageRank value. We predict paper0s rank of citations number and\nPageRank value in the future by writers0 authority value and citer0s authority value. Experimental results show that as\ncompared with FutureRank, our algorithm not only shortens the computing time but also improves the forecast accuracy.', '0', 0, 0, '38', '10', '1654-1662', NULL, '', 1.5, '刘大有，薛锐青，齐红', 't', '62', '无'),
(94, 'Panoramic Virtual Field Geological Information System Based on RIA', 'uploadFile/fc4f787e-5b32-46b9-bf25-9a3bdd9e84e0.pdf', '2011年底统计时论文和检索尚未出来', 75, 75, 47, '2012-12-01 06:39:54', '2012-12-10', '1', 'EECM2011', '2012-05', 'IBR, RIA, Geoscience Data, Geological Information System', '虚拟现实技术改善了现有地质信息系统的可视性和交互性，但是由于地质数据自身的特点，使得实时性成为新系统的瓶颈。RIA技术为此提供了一个新的解决方法。论文分析了相关技术带来的机遇，并以吉林大学辽宁兴城野外地质教研基地为例，设计并实现了一个三维全景虚拟野外地质信息系统，有效改善了现有系统的可视性、交互性和实时性。', 'The technology of Virtual Reality (VR) could improve the visualization and the interactivity of the existing Geological Information System effectively, but the real-time performance becomes the bottle-neck of such integration system because of both the large and complex geoscience data and the huge computation of constructing virtual environment. Rich Internet Applications (RIA) provides a new solution to this problem. The author analyzes the opportunities brought by these two computer technologies and implements a three-dimension panoramic virtual field Geological Information System as a demonstration system for the XingCheng field geological teaching and studying base of Jilin University, which could manage, analyze and manipulate the panoramic geological images and related geoscience data. Practice shows that it not only improves the visualization and the interactivity of the existing Geological Information System but also solves the bottle-neck of real-time performance efficiently.', '20120514736155', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-12-24', '北京', 0.25, 'Chunyan Deng, Linfu Xue, Jinxin He, Wenqing Li, Zhiguo Zhou', 't', '63', '2011年底统计时论文和检索尚未出来'),
(95, '基于隐Markov模型的RNA二级结构预测新方法', 'uploadFile/07ca6948-3cce-4f00-af97-e8c4e604eedd.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b5971b574M2679prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 256, 256, 45, '2012-12-02 08:10:37', '2012-12-07', '1', '计算机研究与发展', '2012-04', '生物信息学，RNA二级结构，假结，自由能，HMM', '有效预测RNA的二级结构是生物信息学中的重要研究领域. 本文给出了一种基于隐马尔科夫模型预测RNA二级结构的新方法。本文应用前后缀匹配算法快速找到所有可能（包括假结）的茎区，建立RNA-HMM，寻找最优的茎区组合方法，得到包含假结的RNA二级结构。实验结果表明，本方法降低了计算复杂性，提高了预测的特异性和敏感性，具有较高的准确率，可以预测假结结构，尤其是tRNA类型的序列执行起来速度较快。', 'The effective prediction of RNA secondary structure is an important research field of bioinformatics. In this paper, we proposed a new method which was based on hidden Markov model to predict the RNA secondary structure. In this paper, we applied the algorithm of the prefix and suffix matching to find all the possible (including the pseudo-knot) stem zones quickly, established the RNA-HMM, found the optimal method of the combination of stem zones, and obtained the RNA secondary structure including the pseudo-knot. The experiment results showed that this method reduced the computational complexity and improved the specificity and sensitivity of prediction, with high accuracy, and can predict the pseudo-knot structure, especially executed faster of the tRNA type sequences.', '20122215069743', 0, 0, '49（4）', '2012年04期', '812-817', NULL, '', 1.5, '董浩，刘元宁，张浩，王刚', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b5971b574M2679prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(97, 'The Design of Embedded Video System Based Boa', 'uploadFile/5b7236ca-d84d-4af6-ae23-603ac16c7ba3.pdf', '1', 267, 68, 47, '2012-12-02 11:27:49', '2012-12-11', '1', 'The 2nd International Conference on Computer Science and Service System', '2012-08', 'Video surveillance；V4L； Boa server； Embedded system', 'The thesis design and implementation of an embedded remote monitoring system Boa server to ARM9 S3C2440 processor core, expanding peripheral devices, using embedded Linux as the operating system, using V4L programming interface for USB camera to capture image information collected, Monitoring information using a wireless network card will be sent. Collection and monitoring of client-side wireless network connection through the WLAN, the access through the Internet, greatly expanded the scope of monitoring. In the monitoring client browser using CGI technology to display images in order to achieve remote monitoring.', 'The thesis design and implementation of an embedded remote monitoring system Boa server to ARM9 S3C2440 processor core, expanding peripheral devices, using embedded Linux as the operating system, using V4L programming interface for USB camera to capture image information collected, Monitoring information using a wireless network card will be sent. Collection and monitoring of client-side wireless network connection through the WLAN, the access through the Internet, greatly expanded the scope of monitoring. In the monitoring client browser using CGI technology to display images in order to achieve remote monitoring.', '1', 1, 1, '', '', '', '2012-08-14', 'China', 0.25, 'Zhao Hongwei，Chen Xiao，Li Zhuo, Bao Huanyu', 't', '62', '1'),
(98, 'The FPGA Verificaition of USB to RS-232 Bridge Controller', 'uploadFile/b778168d-9d2c-458e-88f1-80ae0e74bba7.pdf', '1', 267, 267, 47, '2012-12-02 11:30:51', '2012-12-13', '1', 'The International Conference on Automatic Control and Artificial Intelligence', '2012-03', 'Semiconductor；Bridge Controller；FPGA；Virtual COM', 'The digital circuit of  USB to RS-232 bridge controller is designed; HDL procedure of digital circuit module is download to the FPGA verification board; A driver of the controller which works under the WindowsXP is developed using softwares such as DDK, VC6.0 ,and the virtual COM is realized; Under driver and relevant cooperation of hardware environment , expected the functionsucceed of the controller is realized in the FPGA ;This bridge graft device can be used in the data transmission between serial interface of the mobile phone and USB interface of the computer, reaching the effect of verification.', 'The digital circuit of  USB to RS-232 bridge controller is designed; HDL procedure of digital circuit module is download to the FPGA verification board; A driver of the controller which works under the WindowsXP is developed using softwares such as DDK, VC6.0 ,and the virtual COM is realized; Under driver and relevant cooperation of hardware environment , expected the functionsucceed of the controller is realized in the FPGA ;This bridge graft device can be used in the data transmission between serial interface of the mobile phone and USB interface of the computer, reaching the effect of verification.', '1', 1, 1, '', '', '', '2012-03-24', ' China', 0, 'Sun Fengdong,，Hou Shufan，Zhao Hongwei*，LiangJianguo', 't', '63', '1'),
(99, '一种针对于描述子的SIFT简化方法', 'uploadFile/0b58464f-147a-4933-9b2c-29ec59319bf4.doc', '1', 267, 267, 42, '2012-12-02 11:37:33', '2012-12-10', '1', '仪器仪表学报', '2012-10', 'SIFT；视觉不变量；RANSAC', '由于目前的SIFT特征提取算法具有较高的时间复杂度，不利于大规模的数据存储和搜索，本文提出一种简化的SIFT局部图像特征提取算法。改进的SIFT算法针对于描述子生成部分进行简化，将原算法中特征点描述子的矩形区域改为圆形区域，并将RANSAC算法应用于SIFT特征匹配中，有效地剔除错误匹配点。文中采用K. Mikolajczyk的衡量方法，即查全率和错误率进行评估。实验结果显示，算法在旋转、光照、视角变化等情况下都有很好的匹配效果，并且降低了时间复杂度。', 'As the current SIFT feature extraction algorithm has higher time complexity, so it is not conducive to large-scale data storage and search. So I proposes a simplified SIFT local image feature extraction algorithm. Simplified SIFT algorithm has changed the original algorithm descriptor into sub-circular area, and RANSAC algorithm is applied to SIFT the feature matching. RANSAC algorithm can effective eliminate errors in the match. This paper uses the measure methods of Mikolajczyk k., which is the recall ratio and the error rate. Experimental results show that new algorithm is invariant in rotation, light, perspective change, and reduces the time complexity.', '1', 1, 1, '33', '10', '2255-2262', NULL, '', 0.25, '戴金波,赵宏伟,刘君玲,冯嘉', 't', '62', '1'),
(100, 'Research on Image Retrieval Based on Color and Shape Features', 'uploadFile/21bb9fce-3369-499d-a928-297fe928b632.doc', '已经检索，论文还没邮过来', 267, 274, 47, '2012-12-02 11:45:14', '2012-12-10', '1', ' International Conference on Information Computing and Applications ', '2012-09', 'image retrieval, color features, shape features, color histogram', 'With the robustness of color feature extraction in space and the robustness of shape feature extraction in the displacement transformation, a multi-feature matching algorithm which is combined of color features and shape features is used. In the respect of color feature, some improvements are made to the traditional color histogram method, and a new color histogram method based on main colors is proposed. By combining the major color retrieving method and the color histogram computing, two quick screenings are carried out, thereby the scope of the search is narrowed and the retrieval efficiency is improved. With Fourier shape descriptors adopted, an improved contour-based description method is proposed. Because the tangential angle of contours (curvature) is highlighted and factors such as complex coordinates and center distance are ignored, within a reasonable range, the accuracy is lowered appropriately and the query speed is improved significantly.', 'With the robustness of color feature extraction in space and the robustness of shape feature extraction in the displacement transformation, a multi-feature matching algorithm which is combined of color features and shape features is used. In the respect of color feature, some improvements are made to the traditional color histogram method, and a new color histogram method based on main colors is proposed. By combining the major color retrieving method and the color histogram computing, two quick screenings are carried out, thereby the scope of the search is narrowed and the retrieval efficiency is improved. With Fourier shape descriptors adopted, an improved contour-based description method is proposed. Because the tangential angle of contours (curvature) is highlighted and factors such as complex coordinates and center distance are ignored, within a reasonable range, the accuracy is lowered appropriately and the query speed is improved significantly.', '20124315601108', 1, 1, '', '', '', '2012-09-14', 'China', 0.25, 'Zhao Hongwei，Chen Xiao，Huang Wei，Liu Pingping, Ma Lingjiao', 't', '63', '已经检索，论文还没邮过来'),
(101, 'Learning NT Bayesian Classifier Based on Canonical Cover Analysis of Relational Database.', 'uploadFile/533b332d-70cb-4706-89fa-6e08d788a2d1.pdf', 'http://www.information-iii.org/abs_e2.html#No10-2012', 6, 6, 49, '2012-12-02 12:35:11', '2012-12-09', '1', 'Information: An International Interdisciplinary Journal', '2012-01', 'functional dependency; knowledge discovery，Naive Bayes，canonical cover，conditional', '　　如何将关系数据库函数依赖结合到概率模型的学习过程是知识发现的一个难题。本文提出一种新颖的贝叶斯模型命名nb-tan(NT),采用朴素贝叶斯的条件独立假设并试图维持属性之间相互依赖。因此取得模型复杂性和易学性之间的平衡。并采用正则覆盖将属性集分割为若干相互关联的集合并找到冗余属性。这有助于降低计算复杂度并提升算法的鲁棒性。', 'How to combine functional dependencies of relational database into probabilistic model learning procedure\nis a tough problem for knowledge discovery. This paper presents a novel Bayesian model named NB-TAN (NT),\nwhich utilizes the conditional independence assumption of Naive Bayes while trying to maintain the interdependencies between attributes. Thus a good tradeoff between model complexity and learnability can be\nrealized in practice. Canonical cover is utilized to divide attributes into several related groups and extraneous attributes can be found. This helps to reduce the computational complexity and improve the robustness of the classifier.', '912OO', 0.25, 0, '15', '1', '165-172', NULL, '', 2, 'LiMin Wang, GuoFeng Yao, XiongFei Li', 't', '62', 'http://www.information-iii.org/abs_e2.html#No10-2012'),
(102, 'Extracting Logical Rules and Attribute Subset from Confidence Domain.', 'uploadFile/1a3e029e-6dca-491e-a1ef-c843bd8ca696.pdf', 'http://www.information-iii.org/information_journal.html', 6, 6, 49, '2012-12-02 12:53:26', '2012-12-09', '1', 'INFORMATION-AN INTERNATIONAL INTERDISCIPLINARY JOURNAL', '2012-01', 'artificial intelligence, semi-supervised learning, confidence domain,functional dependency rules of', '逻辑规则已成为在人工智能和知识发现领域流行的提供一个人类理解知识的自然方法。本文提出的SLRFD算法将训练集分为两部分,信任域和非信任域。信任域将训练样本转换为逻辑规则并在半监督学习框架分配测试样本的类标签。基于阿姆斯特朗的公理推导了概率函数依赖规则,用于降低数据的分类维度并不牺牲样本的辨析能力。\n', 'Logical rules have become popular in artificial intelligence and knowledge discovery to provide a natural\nway for humans to understand knowledge. The SLRFD algorithm proposed in this paper divides the training set\ninto two parts, confidence domain and non-confidence domain. The confidence domain is used to translate\ntraining samples into logical rules and assign class labels to testing samples in the semi-supervised learning\nframework. Functional dependency rules of probability are deduced based on Armstrong''s axioms to serve the\npurpose of semantics-preserving data dimensionality reduction for classification without sacrificing the ability to discern between samples belonging to different classes.', '912OO', 0.25, 0, '15', '1', '173-180', NULL, '', 2, 'LiMin Wang, GuoFeng Yao, XiongFei Li', 't', '63', 'http://www.information-iii.org/information_journal.html'),
(103, 'Bayesian Network Inference Based on Functional Dependency Mining of Relational Database', 'uploadFile/fdd13fc9-c9b9-44ab-98c2-8cd0e6a2d7a6.pdf', 'http://www.information-iii.org/information_journal.html', 6, 6, 49, '2012-12-02 13:10:44', '2012-12-09', '1', 'INFORMATION-AN INTERNATIONAL INTERDISCIPLINARY JOURNAL', '2012-06', 'Association rule,Functional dependency, Candidate key, Bayesian network', '为了构建健壮且灵活的贝叶斯网络,本文提出了根据概率函数依赖规则来创建候选关键字和删除冗余属性。每个样本蕴含的函数依赖将基于关联规则挖掘技术被发现。相应的学习算法,即FDBC(基于贝叶斯网络分类器的函数依赖),放松了条件独立性假设的同时保持属性间的依赖关系。实验证明了算法的有效性和高效性。', 'In order to construct robust and flexible Bayesian network, this paper proposed functional dependency rules of probability to create candidate key and delete extraneous attributes. The functional dependencies implicated in each sample will be found based on association rule mining technique in the context of classification. The corresponding learning algorithm, namely FDBC (Functional Dependency based Bayesian network Classifier), relaxes the assumption of conditional independence while maintaining inter-dependencies between attributes. Experimental results are presented to show the effectiveness and efficiency of the proposed approach.', '965MS', 0.25, 0, '15', '6', '2441-2446', NULL, '', 2, 'LiMin Wang, GuoFeng Yao, XiongFei Li', 't', '62', 'http://www.information-iii.org/information_journal.html'),
(104, '一种半球面方位关系表示模型', 'uploadFile/d8b3cc78-3d8f-441d-91a9-f3b6d35ae2d7.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5aeb084dM308aprod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 240, 240, 42, '2012-12-02 14:34:13', '2012-12-10', '1', '人工智能与模式识别', '2012-02', '位关系，半球面，最小边界扇区', '一种表达半球面方位关系的模型——最小边界扇区模型(MBS)，将半球面上区域自上而下正投影到\n底面，且根据参考对象在底面的投影位置，将投影面划分为12个原子区域．根据研究区域占原子区域的个数等信\n息来刻画区域间方位关系，不但可表达出左右等方位关系，还可通过区域上点到中心的距离关系定性表达半球面\n上区域的高度关系等信息．给出MBS模型中可能存在的1 932种情形．为进一步研究MBS模型下的推理及复合表\n的构造，给出此模型下的关系矩阵表示方法，通过此关系矩阵亦可方便推知原半球面上区域间的方位关系．', 'A Minimum Bounding Sector model(MBS)is proposed which represents the direction relationship\non hemispherical surface．The model projects the region on the hemispherical surface to the bottom and\ndivides the bottom region into 12 atom areas based on the projection of the region on the hemispherical\nsurface．In this way，the model not only represents the direction relations such as left and right，but also\nrepresents the height information qualitatively by means of the distance between the points and the center\non the projection plane．And the 1932 cases that exists in the MBS is also represented．As to the further\nresearch on reasoning and the composition table，the relational matrix is proposed through which the\ndirection relations between regions Oil the hemispherical surface are deduced conveniently．', 'EI 20123815454182', 0.515, 8, '25 ', '01', '11~15', NULL, '', 0.25, '欧阳继红，刘玉峰', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5aeb084dM308aprod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(105, '带双洞区域与简单区域间的拓扑关系表示', 'uploadFile/bc70d3a9-9758-4b59-901b-6e78e0965337.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b5ad65638M272cprod1con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=4&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 240, 240, 42, '2012-12-02 14:52:24', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉大学报（工学版）', '2012-09', '拓扑关系，带洞区域，交集矩阵模型', '研究了带双洞区域与简单区域间的空间拓扑关系。给予RCC5通过扩咱4-交集模型矩阵得到了16-交集模型，一个带双洞区域可以视为简单区域A及包含在其中的两个简单B和C，由16-交集矩阵模型可以得到带双洞区域与简单区域间的70中可实现的拓扑关系，并证明了这70中拓扑关系之间的护士完备性。通过比较可知，比RCC-5关系描述的拓扑关系更为细致，表达能力更强。', 'The topological relations between a region with two holes and a simple region were studied. First, we extend 4-intersection matrix model to 16-intersection matrix model to represent the spatial relations of four simple regions, a region with two holes can be seen as a simple region A and two simple regions B and C included in A. Then, a region with two holes and simple region can be seen as four simple regions satisfying certain restricted conditions. Consequently, we obtain 70 topological relations between region with two holes and a simple region in practice by programs and we prove that these topological relations are exclusive and complete. Moreover, compared to the topological relations given by RCC-5 in pairs, the 16-intersection matrix model has stronger expressive ability.', '20124415622999', 1.096, 9, '42', '5', '1214-1218', NULL, '', 0.25, '李健，欧阳继红，王振鑫', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b5ad65638M272cprod1con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=4&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(106, 'Similarity of direction relations in spatial scenes', 'uploadFile/3bf0228e-8806-4ff6-a1d6-e9cc7ec055c1.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3cM2b77prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 240, 240, 41, '2012-12-02 15:17:35', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Computational Information Systems', '2012-10', 'Direction relation matrixes ，Map comparison ，Qualitative direction relations ', '基于方位关系矩阵，本文提出了一种算法，用以度量空间场景方位关系的相似性。', 'Qualitative direction relations can make more concisely and intuitively description of spatial scenes. Similarity of direction relations is important in spatial-scene querying and matching. Similarity assessment of quantitative direction relations needs large amount of calculation and the existing qualitative method does not always work well. For the two issues, based on direction relation matrix, the assignment problem and the transportation algorithm, we propose a method to measure the similarity of qualitative direction relations and implement the similarity assessment algorithm SA-DRM; on this basis, the testing scenarios of quantitative direction relations is used as the benchmark to test SA-DRM, the results verify the effectiveness of this algorithm. Comparing with the quantitative method and the existing qualitative one, our approach is not only much simpler and easier to be implemented than the quantitative one, but also has a better result than the existing qualitative method. Actually, this work is applicable in the area of map comparison, image retrieval etc. ', '20124515655464', 1.2, 9, '8', '20', '8589-8596', NULL, '', 2, 'Sun Wei，Ouyang Jihong，Huo Linlin，Li Shuang', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3cM2b77prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(107, 'Modeling direction relations between uncertain regions', 'uploadFile/3891d136-f89b-4e32-b06f-1f347b52c75a.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b5ad65638M1e4cprod1con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=3&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 240, 240, 41, '2012-12-02 15:24:58', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Computational Information Systems', '2012-10', 'Constraint rule,Decision algorithms,Decision method, Direction relation matrixes, Realizability,Relation matrix,Uncertainty ', 'Uncertainty is almost everywhere in the real world. Two existing models of approximate direction relations are direction relation matrices proposed by Cicerone and the 4-tuples model. Direction relation matrices are not proposed formally, and the decision method of their realizability does not always work well. On the other hand, the realizability decision method of the 4-tuples model is too complicated to be accomplished arithmetically. On these issues, DRMRB is proposed in this paper, then we present and certify the constraint rules of it; based on these rules, the constraint algorithm Realizability-Con () is implemented to obtain the realizable relations. Comparing with the two existing models, we find that DRMRB does not only have better results than the direction relation matrices; but it is also as expressive as the 4-tuples model and the decision algorithm of DRMRB is much simpler and easier to be achieved.', 'Uncertainty is almost everywhere in the real world. Two existing models of approximate direction relations are direction relation matrices proposed by Cicerone and the 4-tuples model. Direction relation matrices are not proposed formally, and the decision method of their realizability does not always work well. On the other hand, the realizability decision method of the 4-tuples model is too complicated to be accomplished arithmetically. On these issues, DRMRB is proposed in this paper, then we present and certify the constraint rules of it; based on these rules, the constraint algorithm Realizability-Con () is implemented to obtain the realizable relations. Comparing with the two existing models, we find that DRMRB does not only have better results than the direction relation matrices; but it is also as expressive as the 4-tuples model and the decision algorithm of DRMRB is much simpler and easier to be achieved.', '20124515645100', 1.2, 7, '8', '19', '8025-8032', NULL, '', 2, 'Sun Wei, Ouyang Jihong; Huo Linlin; Li Shuang', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b5ad65638M1e4cprod1con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=3&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(108, 'Interval-valued fuzzy description logic IFALCN', 'uploadFile/6908b269-7648-4d7b-a90d-6e2b36805d63.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5aeb084dM22c8prod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=7&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 240, 240, 41, '2012-12-02 15:32:15', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal  of Computational Information Systems', '2012-12', 'Fuzzy description logic ，Fuzzy information ，Human cognition ，Interval-valued，Interval-valued fuzzy sets，Tableaux algorithm ，Uncertainty ', 'Classical Description Logics are not suitable to represent interval-valued fuzzy information which exists in many applications. To represent interval-valued fuzzy information, this paper proposes an interval-valued Fuzzy Description Logic, termed as IFALCN, by extending the classical description logic ALCN based on interval-valued fuzzy set. The syntax, semantics and fuzzy tableaux algorithm are presented in detail. We have proved that the proposed algorithm is sound and complete and the consistency of IFALCN ABoxes is PSpace-complete. IFALCN is more expressive than FALCN because the traditional fuzzy description logic FALCN is a special case of IFALCN. The results of representation and reasoning in IFALCN consist with the uncertainty and fuzziness of human cognition better. ', 'Classical Description Logics are not suitable to represent interval-valued fuzzy information which exists in many applications. To represent interval-valued fuzzy information, this paper proposes an interval-valued Fuzzy Description Logic, termed as IFALCN, by extending the classical description logic ALCN based on interval-valued fuzzy set. The syntax, semantics and fuzzy tableaux algorithm are presented in detail. We have proved that the proposed algorithm is sound and complete and the consistency of IFALCN ABoxes is PSpace-complete. IFALCN is more expressive than FALCN because the traditional fuzzy description logic FALCN is a special case of IFALCN. The results of representation and reasoning in IFALCN consist with the uncertainty and fuzziness of human cognition better. ', '20122215069882', 1.2, 2, '8', '7', '3027-3034', NULL, '', 2, 'Linlin Huo, Jihong Ouyang, Wei Sun, Dayou Liu', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M61f0c9ae13b5aeb084dM22c8prod2con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=7&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes');
