(109, 'A novel method of medical image fusion based on bidimensional empirical mode decomposition', 'uploadFile/e1c2dcac-5bf3-4cf6-b70f-1d20af1b9a9c.kdh', '去年未申报', 133, 133, 41, '2012-12-03 01:13:54', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Convergence Information Technology', '2012-01', '医学图像', '略', '略', 'EI：20115214650619', 0, 0, '6', '12', '84-91', NULL, '', 2, 'Feng Kongsen, Zhang Xiaoli,Li Xiongfei☆', 't', '62', '去年未申报'),
(110, 'The ontology architecture of vehicular delay-tolerant network', 'uploadFile/62acafea-3dbd-4cb7-bee5-a3568b3a19e2.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=5&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 41, '2012-12-03 02:36:29', '2012-12-10', '1', 'International Journal of Advancements in Computing Technology', '2012-01', 'Network architecture', '容迟网络', 'Vehicular Delay-Tolerant Network(VDTN) is a new application of the Delay-Tolerant Network(DTN) concept, where vehicles cooperate with each other, acting as the network architecture, to handle non-real time communications at low-cost asynchronous opportun istic conditions. Although increasing kinds of semantic technologies, such as late binding and endpoint ID, have been applied in the application of VDTN, there are few network architectures to consider the semantic technologies. This paper proposes a semantic architecture for VDTNs, using ontology model, based on the hierarchic ontologies. It presents the knowledge shared by different layers and supports each layer''s semantic technologies used. This paper provides a deep understanding of the semantic characteristics of VDTN, leading to insights for future theoretic study.', '20123715422398', 0, 23, '4', '15', '81-88', NULL, '', 2, 'Zhang, Chijun，Yang, Yongjian; Wang, Zhengxuan; Du, Zhanwei; Gao, Yan', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=5&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(111, 'LBS ontologies and its application in DTN', 'uploadFile/485f9009-e7b8-4be5-8fba-5ee3899c756f.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=6&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 41, '2012-12-03 02:40:32', '2012-12-10', '1', 'International Journal of Advancements in Computing Technology', '2012-01', 'Network protocols', '移动网络服务', 'Mobile networking services need the location information, especially in mobile-based DTN. In order to realize the efficient resource searching in mobile-based DTN, we need a mechanism on the basis of contextual information, which can increase the searching efficiency with searching a group of nodes using few messages. So in this paper, we propose two service ontologies for mobile-based networks, called LBSO. Additionally, we propose a Mobile-based routing protocol using the above ontology model for resource searching. While these ideas are simple, our experiments show they significantly raise the delivery rate and lower latency in a wide variety of scenarios as compared to previous approaches.', '20123715422394', 0, 19, '4', '14', '47-56', NULL, '', 2, ' Zhang, Chijun ，Yang, Yongjian; Wang, Zhengxuan; Du, Zhanwei; Gao, Yan', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=6&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(112, 'Intelligent supervision and tracing system for food quality under the internet of things', 'uploadFile/9a1b673a-6d66-4945-9d77-983b14ef7aa2.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=7&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 41, '2012-12-03 02:45:34', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Computational Information Systems', '2012-01', 'Cryptography', '物联网下的智能对食品质量的监督和跟踪系统', 'With the growing of the food industry, some issues about food quality and safety have become a matter of great concern. it was difficult to track and target food quality problems mainly due to poor traditional technology, which was difficult to achieve automatic monitoring of the circulation of the whole process of food production. The emergence of the Internet of Things technology could compensate for the deficiencies of the traditional technology. We proposed an intelligent system for food quality supervision and tracing of the whole process of food production based on the Internet of Things called ISTS. The architecture and functional structure design of ISTS was described based on the requirement analysis in this paper. In the implementation, we presented the data fusion method based on rough set and building methods of food quality analysis model by theory of ontology based on context modeling, and the encryption and anti-fake method of two-dimensional code for food package based on commercial secret and digital watermark technology. The system could basically satisfy the requirements of food quality supervision and tracing through the test. ? 2012 Binary Information Press.', '20123915472580', 0, 17, '8', '17', '7113-7120', NULL, '', 2, 'Jia, Bing; Yang, Yongjian ; Cui, Chunsheng; Li, Li', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=7&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(113, 'Study on learner modeling in adaptive learning system', 'uploadFile/d81e1cb1-12c2-4b4e-9da9-73d1f6551fdd.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 41, '2012-12-03 02:49:56', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Computers (Finland)', '2012-01', 'Learning systems', '智能住宅对学习者的自适应学习系统的建模研究', 'In light of the present situation research on learner model in Adaptive Learning System at home and abroad, This paper summarizes the main problems of learner model, such as the unscientific attention dimension, poor calculated representation method and single and subjective method to obtain Characteristic value. So this paper has put forward a new learner model to achieve selforganization and push of learning resources on the basis of learning goals and learner''s personal conditions. It includes three characteristic items such as knowledge level, cognitive ability and preferences. We respectively introduce the representation and acquisition of characteristic value of learner model in detail. After that, we propose a new Adaptive Learning System based on this learner model as a case. Experimental results show this learner model is effective and practical in the application', '20124415634492', 0, 15, '7', '10', '2585-2592', NULL, '', 2, 'Jia, Bing; Yang, Yongjian; Zhang, Jun ', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b5af42f3c6a95prod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(114, 'Cross-layer routing metric for wireless mesh networks', 'uploadFile/3058ea5f-a5e3-444a-9d0a-9669c7dcd54b.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b5e1ab5b6M1857prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 47, '2012-12-03 02:55:23', '2012-12-10', '1', 'ICICA 2012, Proceedings', '2012-01', 'Wireless mesh networks (WMN)', '跨层路由度量的无线网状网络', 'To meet the shortage of the typically routing metrics used in wireless mesh network, this paper proposed a new routing metric for wireless mesh network-CAETT (Congestion Avoidance Expected Transmission Time), comparing with several other routing metrics. With the queue''s utilization rate and the transmit situation of control frames in 802.11 protocol''s MAC layer, a reasonable path is chosen in terms of the channel competition status, link data frame delivery rate and the node''s queue utilization rate. After that the advantages of this new routing metric and its applications were discussed. Finally the simulation experiments show the good network performance', '20124315590090', 0, 10, '', '', '', '2012-09-14', 'Chengde, China', 0.25, 'Li, Xiang; Yang, Yong-Jian; Cui, Chun-Sheng; Yang, Guan-Nan', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=61bdc4fa13b5e1ab5b6M1857prod4con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=2&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(115, 'The construction of security supervision platform for fireworks and firecrackers based on IOT', 'uploadFile/4150fcb0-45ac-42fe-a26f-1d2d82dd4f3f.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M7c7eb8b913b5e747366M4bacprod2con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 284, 284, 47, '2012-12-03 02:59:00', '2012-12-10', '1', ' Applied Mechanics and Materials,', '2012-01', 'Algorithms', '烟花爆竹安全监管平台建设的基础上IOT', 'Lacking effective management means for production, storage, transportation, marketing and other aspects is the existing problems in the current fireworks and firecrackers security supervision. We propose a design method on constructing the safety supervision platform of the whole process of fireworks and firecrackers production with the background of the emerging Internet of Things (IOT for short), the use of RFID technology, combined with the 3G networks, GPS/GIS, video camera technology to constitute the architecture of the platform. In this article, we also present the crucial technology of constructing the platform and relevant implementation, including the associated matching algorithms between the RFID tags and two dimensional codes, building methods of fireworks and firecrackers quality model by theory of ontology-based context modeling. It achieves full supervision and traceability management in production, storage, transportation, wholesale and retail. And it can provide summary statistics and on-site real-time dynamic queries', '20124215573188', 0, 5, '', '', '', '2012-08-01', 'Guangxi, China', 0.25, 'Jia, Bing;,Yang, Yongjian ,Cui, Chunsheng', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M7c7eb8b913b5e747366M4bacprod2con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(117, '基于均值偏移粒子滤波的自适应跟踪', 'uploadFile/82f4be91-4efa-405f-9c2f-385ed0d50fde.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=3&CurRec=5&recid=&filename=JLGY201202028&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 42, '2012-12-03 06:23:37', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报（工学版）', '2012-03', '计算机应用，自适应跟踪，均值偏移粒子滤波，高斯噪声方差', '针对视频中运动人体的跟踪，提出了一种基于均值偏移粒子滤波的自适应跟踪算法。该算法首先对所要跟踪的人体目标进行分块，并选择与周围环境颜色相似度最小的块模板作为跟踪区域；然后使用基于均值偏移的粒子滤波方法进行跟踪，并设计了自适应更新块模板尺度的方法；最后在粒子滤波的状态估计阶段后，加入自适应观测模型，根据块模板尺度的变\n化情况，自适应地选择高斯噪声方差和粒子数目。实验证明，在出现遮挡或人体运动方向改变的情况下，本文算法的跟踪效果比传统均值偏移粒子滤波更好。', 'An adaptive tracking algorithm based on the combination of particle filter and mean shift is proposed. First, the tracking target is segmented into different block templates, and the block template with the least color similarity to the surroundings is chosen as a tracking region. Then, the block template is adjusted adaptively to the best scale when it is tracked by the proposed particle filter method based on the mean shift. Finally, an adaptive observation model is introduced after the state estimation of particle filter, and the Gaussian noise variance and the number of particles are determined according to the change of the block template scale. Experimental results show that the performance of the proposed algorithm is better than traditional method when target body is partially occluded or its moving direction is changed.', '20121514937735', 0, 1, '42', '2', '407-411', NULL, '', 0.25, '李文辉，周强，王莹，张德才', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=3&CurRec=5&recid=&filename=JLGY201202028&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(118, '基于视频的全天候多特征融合火焰检测算法', 'uploadFile/cb404291-f455-41d5-abe4-005ebb780bb2.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=0&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201203032&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 44, '2012-12-03 06:47:45', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(理学版)', '2012-05', '视频类型判断, 全天候,火焰检测,特征融合, 红外视频', '针对传统可视化火灾探测技术采用单独分析可见光摄像设备或红外摄像设备采集的图像进行火灾探测，不能全天候监控火焰的问题，提出一种全天候多特征融合的检测算法． 首先通过视频类型判断算法确定摄像头采集的每帧图像类型，然后利用与图像类型相对应的算法提取疑似火焰区域，最后对疑似区域进行基于DCT 的火焰频率检测和帧间相关性检测，判断火焰是否存在,实验表明，该检测算法解决了传统可视化探测技术不能全天候监控火焰的问题，且能在保持火焰高检测率的同时降低误检率．', 'A multi-feature fusion flame detection algorithm using video-type judgment algorithm was proposed．\nIn this algorithm，the video-type of each frame was first judged． Then candidate flame region was extracted bythe algorithm that corresponds image types，at last the flame frequency feature based on DCT and imagecorrelation feature between frames in the candidate region were detected to determine the existence of flame.The traditional visualization fire detection technology is basically based on analyzing the images from infrared cameras or visible camera to detect flame． The method can not meet the requirements of round-the-clock monitoring flame in engineering application．Experiments show that the proposed detection algorithm can resolve this problem，detect flame fast and reduce the error rate．', 'N/A', 0, 0, '50', '3', '527-534', NULL, '', 0.25, '李文辉，刘培勋，王莹，肖林厂，王聪', 't', '63', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=0&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201203032&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(119, '使用日夜两用型红外摄像机进行火焰检测', 'uploadFile/ab600318-0eb0-4db9-a217-0a10e901f1e7.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=0&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=HNDX201208015&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 42, '2012-12-03 06:48:59', '2012-12-10', '1', '湖南大学学报（自然科学版）', '2012-08', '火灾科学，计算机视觉，火焰检测，全天候监控', '为了提高火灾监控的准确性和及时性,并最大限度地利用已有硬件设备,提出一种使用日夜两用型红外摄像机的火灾自动监控方法.根据红外图像RGB空间的色彩分布特点,设计视频类型判断算法,实现视频图像类型自动切换.通过红外状态与可见光状态两类状态下的焰色模型提取火焰疑似区域.对疑似火焰区域提取不规则度、角点量、闪烁频率和帧间相关性等4个静态及动态检测特征.通过减聚类和模糊C均值聚类相融合的方式优化训练样本,并分别训练2种状态下的火焰识别神经网络分类器.实验结果表明:视频类型判别平均准确率93.07%,21段火焰或干扰视频均能正确检测,报警时间小于8s,帧处理速度达到25帧/s以上.对室内自动火灾监控的精度高、抗干扰能力强、处理速度实时和适应全天候监控等. ', 'In order to improve the accuracy and timeliness of fire detection and achieve the optimal utilization of existing hardware equipments, an automatic fire detection method with day-night infrared camera was proposed. Firstly, a video category classification algorithm based on IR frame color distribution in RGB color space was proposed. It can classify different videos and switch the detection state automatically. Then, fire candidate regions were extracted by using the fire color models of infrared state and visible state. Thirdly, the irregularity, corner number, frequency and correlation coefficient oscillation times were computed as four static or dynamic fire features. Finally, the training feature data optimized by Subtractive Clustering and Fuzzy C Means were the input of Neural Network,and fire classifiers for two kinds of video states were trained separately. Experiment results have indicated that the average classification accuracy of video categories has achieved 93.07%, and the proposed method is able to detect all of the 21 videos correctly. The proposed method gives warning 8 seconds after fire occurs. The processing speed is more than 25fps. It can meet the requirements of high detection precision, strong anti-interference, realtime processing speed, and adaptation to alleather monitoring.', '20124315599635', 0, 0, '39', '8', '73-80', NULL, '', 0.25, '李文辉，王莹，赵瑞霖，刘培勋，倪洪印，肖林厂 ', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=0&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=HNDX201208015&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(120, '对码本模型中码字结构的改进', 'uploadFile/6e76352a-8ec7-4a1c-995a-1e546516a84e.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=4&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201203030&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 44, '2012-12-03 06:53:00', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(理学版)', '2012-05', '运动目标检测,码本模型,码字结构,5元组码字', '针对码本结构，提出一种简化算法． 该算法通过将码字元组中判断该码字是否冗余的元素最大未使用时间改为由元组的其他变量直接计算而不存储在码字中，去除了该变量所占用的空间，将6 元组替换为5 元组。实验结果表明，该改进不会对运动目标检测增加额外计算，准确性和实时性不受影响，并可减少码本模型占用的内存．', 'The codeword space was reduced according to calculating the longest interval so that codeword is never recurred by other variable in tuple，and the interval is not stored in codeword，thus 6-tuple basedcodeword is replaced by 5-tuple． The experimental result shows that the new codebook model is as fast and accurate as the original model． Moreover，the memory space demanded is reduced．', 'N/A', 0, 0, '50', '3', '517-522', NULL, '', 0.25, '李文辉，李慧春，王莹，姜园媛，孙明玉', 't', '63', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=4&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201203030&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(121, '基于环境遮挡掩码的物理正确柔和阴影绘制算法', 'uploadFile/38f21199-912b-47b4-9577-f6f56565bb10.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=7&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY201204033&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 42, '2012-12-03 06:55:36', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(工学版)', '2012-07', '计算机应用，柔和阴影，环境遮挡，光源可见性，绘制方程', '针对物理正确的柔和阴影绘制问题,提出一种使用环境遮挡掩码来实现面光源可见性计算的方法。在绘制前,预先创建一个环境遮挡掩码立方图。在绘制过程中,利用环境遮挡掩码立方图来计算所有与可见性测试四棱锥相交的三角形面片的环境遮挡掩码,并对它们作"与"运算,再通过遮挡距离测试操作即可求出哪些光源采样光线不受遮挡。与蒙特卡洛积分光照计算方法相比,本文方法不但能绘制出物理正确的柔和阴影,而且避免了大量的阴影光线求交测试操作,提高了绘制方程的求解效率。', 'Focusing on the problem of rendering physically correct soft shadows, a method is proposed which uses occlusion masks to evaluate the visibility of an area light source. Prior to the rendering process, a cube map of ambient occlusion masks is computed. In the rendering process, the cube map is employed to compute the ambient occlusion masks of triangles intersecting with a rectangular pyramid, which is used as the bounding volume for light-source sample rays in the visibility testing. Then the "and" bitwise operations are carried out on these ambient occlusion masks. Finally, based on the results of the bitwise operations, the blocking-distance testing is further utilized to determine which light-source sample rays are not blocked. Compared with the lighting computation method via Monte Carlo integration, the proposed method can not only render physically correct soft shadows, but also avoid a large number of intersection-testing operations for shadow rays. This advantage can enhance the efficiency in solving the rendering equation.', '20123515381261', 0, 0, '42', '4', '971-978', NULL, '', 0.25, '陈纯毅，杨华民，李文辉，蒋振刚', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=7&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY201204033&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(122, '基于模糊聚类分析和多特征融合的人脸识别方法', 'uploadFile/35e8d74d-833c-4744-8c17-0c2b384711b5.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201202029&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 44, '2012-12-03 06:58:52', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(理学版)', '2012-03', '计算机应用，人脸识别，特征融合，线性子空间， 模糊聚类分析，Gabor 小波', '提出一种使用模糊聚类融合线性子空间特征和Gabor 小波特征的人脸识别方法。通过分析样本在子空间的聚类情况，对处于不同聚类边界的样本采用Gabor 特征进行二次识别。实验结果表明，该方法能在保证识别率的前提下，有效减少平均识别时间。', 'A method of using fuzzy clustering analysis to combine linear subspace features and Gabor features to recognize faces was proposed． Firstly it analyzes the distribution of sample database in linear space.Then it uses Gabor features to recognize faces that locate in boundary of different cluster centers.Experimental results show the presented method has high recognition rate，meanwhile it reduces average recognition time．', 'N/A', 0, 0, '50', '2', '293-298', NULL, '', 0.25, '高璐，李文辉，王莹', 't', '63', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201202029&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(123, '基于帧间虚拟点光源重用的动态场景间接光照近似求解算法', 'uploadFile/0e803271-a61f-436d-9342-36e504982d40.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY2012102201I&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 42, '2012-12-03 07:01:15', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(工学版)', '2012-07', ' 计算机应用，间接光照，虚拟点光源，帧间重用，重要性采样', '基于即时光能辐射度方法的虚拟点光源思想,提出一种新的动态场景间接光照近似求解算法。首先设计出可视场景区域敏感的虚拟点光源采样策略和基于间隔采样的间接光照贡献聚集方法,并给出了它们在GPU上的实现途径。然后提出虚拟点光源的帧间重用与更新方法,实现了对虚拟点光源的帧间失效检测、重建及其抛物面阴影图的更新。本文算法将动态场景当作一个整体处理,无需预先区分和指定静态对象和动态对象。实验结果表明,本文算法能够显著地减少动态场景间接光照的平均计算时间。', 'Based on the idea of virtual point lights used by instant radiosity, a novel algorithm for approximately calculating the indirect illumination of dynamic scenes was proposed. First, the view-sensitive sampling strategy of virtual point lights and the interleaved-sampling based method of indirect illumination gathering were designed, and their GPU implementation was further presented. Second, the method for reusing and updating virtual point lights among consecutive frames was suggested; based on it, the validity testing, the reconstruction and the paraboloid shadow-map update of virtual point lights were realized. Our algorithm treats\nthe dynamic scene as a whole and does not need to obtain the information with respect to static and dynamic objects in advance. Experiment results show that our algorithm can significantly reduce the average computation timings of indirect illumination of dynamic scenes.', '优先出版,尚未检索', 0, 0, '42', '4', 'N/A', NULL, '', 0.25, '陈纯毅， 杨华民，李文辉，蒋振刚', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY2012102201I&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(124, '一种基于块的视频烟雾检测算法', 'uploadFile/e5ce444a-5db1-4dad-af24-343f1d3e2794.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201205033&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 44, '2012-12-03 07:04:19', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报(理学版)', '2012-09', '烟雾检测，运动检测，主运动方向， 运动块，小波变换', '为克服传统探测器的缺点，提高视频烟雾检测算法的检测率，提出一种基于运动块的视频烟雾检测算法． 该算法先采用帧差法提取运动块，再分析由运动块组成连通域的面积和运动估计结果，从而确定疑似烟雾区域． 通过二维离散小波变换提取高、低频能量特征值，并根据运动估计结果提取运动保持特征值，综合各特征值判断是否有烟雾发生． 实验结果表明，该方法能及时检测到烟雾，鲁棒性较高、抗干扰能力强，能有效预防火灾．', 'In order to overcome the shortcomings of conventional detectors and improve the detection rate of\nthe current smoke detection algorithms，a new smoke detection approach based on motion block was proposed.Firstly，motion blocks were extracted by frame difference method． Then，candidate smoke regions were determined according to the area and the result of the motion estimation of every connected region.Lastly，the high/low frequency energy eigenvalues were obtained via discrete avelet transformation and the movement maintenance eigenvalue was obtained according to the result of the estimated direction of movement.These eigenvalues were used to determine whether there is smoke． The experimental results prove that the proposed algorithm is robust，anti-disturb.It could detect the appearance of smoke timely and prevent fire effectively．', 'N/A', 0, 0, '49', '3', '979-986', NULL, '', 0.25, '李文辉，肖林厂，王莹，傅博，刘培勋', 't', '63', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLDX201205033&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(125, '基于尺度不变特征变换的平面旋转人脸检测', 'uploadFile/1cb3de40-4d4c-49c2-b7c7-dc5aa37975cc.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=22&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY20120522008&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=', 175, 175, 42, '2012-12-03 07:08:00', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报（工学版）', '2012-06', ' 计算机应用，SIFT 特征，Adaboost 算法，人脸检测，人脸扶正', '针对平面旋转人脸检测的问题，改进了传统的尺度不变特征变换(SIFT)算法，利用其旋转、缩放、平移及部分仿射不变性完成平面旋转人脸的检测。首先通过模板与对比度加权的方法对 SIFT 关键点进行裁减提高计算效率并过滤无效关键点，并提出一种更精确的主方向计算方法确定关键点主方向，通过 Adaboost 算法训练人脸公共特征分类器并计算关键点的匹配率作为置信权值，完成平面旋转人脸的检测，并根据关键点主方向进行扶正。经试验，本文方法在保证检测率的同时，在扶正精确度、检测速度方面相对于传统方法有较大提高。 ', 'Aiming at the problem of face detection under rotation in image plane, the Scale Invariant Feature Transform(SIFT)algorithm was improved. The SIFT with the invariant of rotation, scale, translation and illumination was used to detect the rotation face in image plane. Firstly, a pruning algorithm of combining the template and contrast was used to increase efficiency and filter the invalid key points, and a higher accuracy main direction algorithm was proposed. Secondly used adaboost algorithm to train a common face classifier and compute the matching ratio of key point. It can detect face under rotation in image plane, and normalize\nthe face by the main direction of key points. The experiment results indicate the new method preserves the high detection ratio, and has a better performance in the normalization precision and detection efficiency.', '优先出版,尚未检索', 0, 0, '42', '4', '优先出版', NULL, '', 0.25, '李根，李文辉', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=22&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY20120522008&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx='),
(126, 'Geometry Compression Method for  Terrain Rendering Method with GPU-Based Error Metric', 'uploadFile/6de2296e-ccb1-402b-8af8-253673019c40.pdf', '2011年发表', 175, 175, 47, '2012-12-03 07:16:47', '2012-12-10', '1', 'VRCAI 2011', '2012-12', 'geometry compression, GPU-based, large-scale terrain', 'null', 'We present a geometry compression method for large-scale terrain rendering, which is based on restricted quadtree meshes. Terrain data of our method are organized by special structure, and then dynamically transmitted to graphic hardware and compute dynamic error metric by GPU, for the purpose of reducing bandwidth requirements and saving the running time of CPU.\n', 'EI 检索号:20120614739900', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-12-11', 'Hong Kong', 0.25, 'Zihou Ge ,Wenhui Li', 't', '63', '2011年发表'),
(127, 'A novel method with adaptive non-local means for image denoising', 'uploadFile/47988dff-f127-4ce6-86d1-f1ee6460357a.pdf', 'http://www.aicit.org/aiss/global/paper_detail.html?jname=AISS&q=1489', 175, 175, 41, '2012-12-03 07:22:19', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Advances in Information Sciences and Service Sciences', '2012-09', 'Non-Local Means, Wavelet Energy, Adaptive Filter Parameter, Mean-Shift Segmentation', 'N/A', 'Non-local means is a hotspot in image denoising. This paper contributes two novel techniques by Non-local means. First, we propose wavelet energy analysis of an adaptive parameter estimation method. Then, we segment the aimed-image into different texture-areas, and estimate parameter c corresponding to different texture-areas. In filtering, the segmented texture-areas can get more contribution values from the same texture-type areas. Practical tests show that the proposed method can obtain more accurate denoising results and higher PSNR comparing with traditional non-local means and non-local means using wavelet.', '20124115548369', 0, 0, '4', '16', '251-257', NULL, '', 2, 'Li,Wen-hui, Fu,Bo, Cui,Chun-ri, Li,Hui-ying, Wang,Ying, Lin,Yi-feng, Ni,Hong-yin,  Wu, Zhen-jing', 't', '62', 'http://www.aicit.org/aiss/global/paper_detail.html?jname=AISS&q=1489'),
(128, 'Fast pedestrian detection with a cascade of multi-Hogs', 'uploadFile/8539971c-ee7b-4509-81ae-a4bae67eb353.pdf', 'http://www.aicit.org/jcit/global/paper_detail.html?jname=JCIT&q=1520', 175, 175, 41, '2012-12-03 07:31:55', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Convergence Information Technology', '2012-07', 'Human Detection, Irregular Rectangle, Hog, Adaboost, Cascade Classifier', 'N/A', 'Accurate and efficient human detection has become an important area for research in computer vision. In order to solve problems in the past human detection algorithms such as features with fixed sizes, fixed positions and fixed number, the human detection based on multi-Hogs algorithm was proposed. A novel representation of irregular rectangles called Vertex-Vector Representation was introduced and generation algorithms of Vertex-Vector Representation and inner points of a new rectangle in the intersection of two irregular rectangles were proposed. Through intersection tests and feature integration, the algorithm can dynamically generate the features closer to human body contours. Basically maintaining the detection speed, the detection accuracy was improved by our algorithm.', '20123215329676', 0, 0, '7', '13', '162-169', NULL, '', 2, 'Wenhui Li, Yifeng Lin, Ying Wang, Hongyin Ni, Wenting Wu, Shoujia Wang', 't', '63', 'http://www.aicit.org/jcit/global/paper_detail.html?jname=JCIT&q=1520'),
(129, 'A Large-scale Terrain Rendering Method with GPU-Based Compression', 'uploadFile/ffa41297-1082-4a79-9425-38928e3a0561.pdf', '2011年发表', 175, 175, 41, '2012-12-03 07:41:10', '2012-12-11', '1', ' Computer Science and Convergence', '2012-12', 'GPU-based, Geometry Compression, Large-Scale terrain rendering, restricted quadtree meshes,', 'null', 'We present a large-scale terrain rendering method, which compressing data are decoded in GPU\nand dynamic error metric are computed by GPU too. The domain was first tiled and computed into a nested\ngeometric space error map and stored into displaying memory with terrain map. At run time, screen space\nerror is projected from geometric error, and compare with error threshold according to view-point, to select\nterrain grid points by GPU. At last, triangle strip is constructed according to RQT method. The error metric\nmethod corresponds to parallel computing requires, and processes the error metric and triangulation by GPU,\nto improve the rending efficiency of image hardware, and save the running time of CPU. For large-scale\nterrain data, we use geometry compression method to reduce data amount transmitted from hard disk to\nmemory, which can be decoded by GPU.', 'EI 检索号:20115214642707', 0, 0, '114', '1', '3-9', NULL, '', 0.25, 'Zihou Ge, Wenhui Li', 't', '62', '2011年发表'),
(130, '基于实际无线环境的无线传感器网络拓扑控制算法', 'uploadFile/39de1921-7e6b-4707-a482-0fb814b75ac7.pdf', 'http://xuebao.jlu.edu.cn/gxb/CN/abstract/abstract11543.shtml#', 3, 3, 42, '2012-12-03 07:47:38', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报（工学版）', '2012-07', '计算机应用，拓扑控制，能量消耗，分布式算法', '提出了一种无需任何位置信息的面向实际无线环境应用的分布式拓扑控制算法(Minimum transmission power based topology control,MPTC),它基于节点最小发射功率计算节点间是否存在每跳能量消耗都小于其直接通信时的能量消耗的多跳路径来构建网络拓扑,在保持网络连通的前提下,降低了网络的能量消耗。仿真结果表明,该算法构建的拓扑具有能量消耗均衡、鲁棒性好等特点。', 'This paper proposes a simple distributed topology control algorithm named Minimum Transmission Power based Topology Control (MPTC). It computes whether there is a multi-hop path between two direct communication nodes with the energy cost across each hop less than that of the two nodes. MPTC reduces the energy consumption while maintaining the network connectivity without the use of location-based information. A simulation-based comparative analysis is presented. The results show that the proposed MPTC has the advantages such as balanced energy consumption and good robust properties.', '20123515381259', 0.371, 0, '第42卷', '第4期', '958-962', NULL, '', 0.25, '胡黄水，秦贵和', 't', '63', 'http://xuebao.jlu.edu.cn/gxb/CN/abstract/abstract11543.shtml#'),
(131, 'Geometry Compression Method for Deformable Terrain Rendering', 'uploadFile/30aa0025-1e82-46ac-ad3b-9aa22e4d939d.pdf', '2012年发表', 175, 175, 46, '2012-12-03 08:01:29', '2012-12-11', '1', 'ICCIT2011', '2012-10', 'GPU-based , Geometry compression , deformable terrain rendering , nested error metric , restricted quadtree meshes ', 'null', 'We present a geometry compression method for deformable terrain rendering method, which dynamically transmit compressing data to graphic hardware and compute dynamic error metric by GPU. The domain is first tiled and computed into a nested geometric space error map, and tiled data are compressed and sorted by space error during preprocessing. Then data are dynamically transmitted into displaying memory according to rendering demand. At run time, compressed data is decoded by GPU and screen space error is projected from geometric error, and compare with error threshold according to view-point, to select terrain grid points by GPU. At last, triangle strip is constructed by comparing with an order array to render terrain. As data are dynamically transmitted according to rendering demand, our method significantly reduces bandwidth requirements in the rendering of deformable terrain.\n\n', 'N/A', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-10-04', 'Seogwipo', 0.25, 'Zihou Ge,Wenhui Li', 't', '62', '2012年发表'),
(132, 'Semi-supervised Bayesian network classifier learning based on interrelation mining among attributes', 'uploadFile/e997e277-295a-411a-97ec-7538635dc1ed.pdf', '国际会议', 6, 6, 47, '2012-12-03 08:01:56', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Proceeding of 2012 International Conference on Uncertainty Reasoning and', '2012-08', 'Semi-supervised learning，Bayesian classification', '半监督学习作为一个有效的模型已经应用到许多研究领域,它也成为机器学习和知识发现研究主要领域。传统上,大多数分类模型构建有监督式学习过程,当测试样本明显超过了训练样本时会导致较高的误差率。本文提出基于半监督学习贝叶斯分类器,它利用所有测试和训练样本挖掘属性相互关系，并放松朴素贝叶斯的条件独立性假设。最后实验结果显示出方法的有效性。\n', 'Semi-supervised Learning as an efficient paradigm has been applied to many research areas, it also becomes one of the research focuses in machine learning and knowledge discovery. Traditionally, most classification models are built by supervised learning procedure, which leads to high rate of misclassification when test samples are significantly more than the training samples. This paper proposed to learn Bayesian classifier by using a semisupervised procedure, which exploits the inter-relations among attributes mined from all test and training samples together to relax the conditional independent assumption of Naive Bayes(NB). Experimental results are presented to show the effectiveness and efficiency of the proposed approach.', '20124515643891', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-08-14', 'Jakarta, Indonesia', 0.25, 'Wang Limin,Xia Huijie,Xu Peijuan', 't', '63', '国际会议'),
(133, '基于OSEK的CAN网络管理模拟平台的设计与实现', 'uploadFile/020acc26-f44e-4130-bd86-1353b9edab71.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=4&CurRec=4&recid=&filename=SJSJ201210053&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJWK2F1dXlNL3hwV0dqbzRmckxseWEwdFFUNmxpeVpjM2ZPcVVQb1RwZ1dock16cw==', 3, 3, 44, '2012-12-03 08:43:50', '2012-12-10', '1', '计算机工程与设计', '2012-10', '控制器局域网； OSEK/VDX，网络管理，网络仿真器，模块扩展', ' 为增强车载总线CAN网络的安全可靠性,满足日益增加的车载电控单元对网络安全性能的需求,深入研究了OS-EK/VDX中的网络管理标准及实现机制,并探讨了在CAN网络中引入OSEK/VDX直接NM(OSEK/VDX direcr NM)机制的可行性。根据CAN网络的通信机制与直接NM的特点,在NS2仿真系统上扩展了CAN网络模块与直接NM模块,并通过实验有效地实现了两者的结合。实验结果表明,OSEK/VDX直接NM系统可在CAN网络中迅速达到稳定状态,继而为CAN网络的安全、可靠运行提供有效保障。', 'Ｔｏ　ｅｎｈａｎｃｅ　ｔｈｅ　ｓｅｃｕｒｉｔｙ　ａｎｄ　ｒｅｌｉａｂｉｌｉｔｙ　ｏｆ　ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ　ｔｈａｔ　ｉｓ　ａ　ｖｅｈｉｃｌｅ　ｂｕｓ，ｓａｔｉｓｆｙ　ｔｈｅ　ｒｅｑｕｉｒｅｍｅｎｔ　ｗｈｉｃｈ　ｉｎｃｒｅａｓｉｎｇ Ｖｅｈｉｃｌｅ　ｅｌｅｃｔｒｏｎｉｃ　ｃｏｎｔｒｏｌ　ｕｎｉｔｓ（ＥＣＵ）ｄｅｍａｎｄ　ｔｏ　ｔｈｅ　ｓａｆｅｔｙ　ｏｆ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ．Ｔｈｅ　ｆｅａｓｉｂｉｌｉｔｙ　ｏｆ　ｔｈｅ　ｍｅｃｈａｎｉｓｍ　ａｎｄ　ｉｍｐｌｅｍｅｎｔａｔｉｏｎ ｍｅｃｈａｎｉｓｍ　ｉｓ　ｄｉｓｃｕｓｓｅｄ　ｉｎ　ｄｅｐｔｈ，ｔｈｅｎ　ｔｈｅ　ＯＳＥＫ／ＶＤＸ　ｄｉｒｅｃｔ　ＮＭ（ＯＳＥＫ／ＶＤＸ　ｄｉｒｅｃｔ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ　ｍａｎａｇｅｍｅｎｔ）ｉｓ　ｉｎｔｒｏｄｕｃｅｄ　ｉｎｔｏ ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ．Ｂａｓｅｄ　ｏｎ　ｔｈｅ　ｆｅａｔｕｒｅｓ　ｏｆ　ｔｈｅ　ｍｅｃｈａｎｉｓｍ　ｏｆ　ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ　ｃｏｍｍｕｎｉｃａｔｉｏｎ　ａｎｄ　ｔｈｅ　ｄｉｒｅｃｔ　ＮＭ，ｔｈｅ　ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ ｍｏｄｕｌｅ　ａｎｄ　ｄｉｒｅｃｔ　ＮＭ　ｍｏｄｕｌｅ　ａｒｅ　ｅｘｔｅｎｄｅｄ　ｉｎ　ＮＳ２．Ｆｕｒｔｈｅｒｍｏｒｅ，ｔｈｅｓｅ　ｔｗｏ　ｐａｒｔｓ　ａｒｅ　ｃｏｍｂｉｎｅｄ　ｅｆｆｅｃｔｉｖｅｌｙ．Ｔｈｅ　ｅｘｐｅｒｉｍｅｎｔ ｐｒｏｖｅｓ　ｔｈａｔ　ｔｈｅ　ＯＳＥＫ／ＶＤＸ　ｄｉｒｅｃｔ　ＮＭ　ｓｙｓｔｅｍ　ｃａｎ　ｇｏ　ｔｏ　ｓｔｅａｄｙ　ｉｎ　ｔｈｅ　ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔｗｏｒｋ　ｉｍｍｅｄｉａｔｅｌｙ，ｔｈｅｎ　ｇｕａｒａｎｔｅｅｓ　ｔｈｅ　ＣＡＮ　ｎｅｔ－ｗｏｒｋ　ｉｎ　ｓｅｃｕｒｉｔｙ　ａｎｄ　ｒｅｌｉａｂｉｌｉｔｙ．', '无', 0.449, 0, '第33卷', '第10期', '3923-3926', NULL, '', 0.25, '秦贵和，叶晨思，陈筠翰，赵耀', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=4&CurRec=4&recid=&filename=SJSJ201210053&dbname=CJFDTEMP&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJWK2F1dXlNL3hwV0dqbzRmckxseWEwdFFUNmxpeVpjM2ZPcVVQb1RwZ1dock16cw=='),
(134, 'Prediction of tRNA based on LS-SVM algorithm with principal component analysis', 'uploadFile/606c4cf9-efa2-461d-ac07-1a5d97caa5f0.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b5f4c4468280prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 115, 113, 47, '2012-12-03 09:09:26', '2012-12-10', '1', '2012 International Conference on Building Materials and Structural Engineering', '2012-03', 'Transfer RNA, Non-coding RNA, Principal component analysis, Least squares support vector machine', '见英文部分', 'Recently, non-coding RNA prediction is the one of the most important researches in\nbioinformatics. In this paper, on the basis of principal component analysis, we present a tRNA\nprediction strategy by using least squares support vector machine (LS-SVM). Appearance frequencies\nof single nucleotide, 2 – nucleotides and (G-C) %, (A-T) % were chosen as characteristics inputs.\nResults from tests showed that the prediction accuracy was 90.51% on prokaryotic tRNA dataset.\nExperimental results indicate that the method is effective for prokaryotic ncRNA prediction.', '20120914821811', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-03-19', '武汉', 0.25, 'Xing Chong, Wang Yao, Zhou You, Liang Yanchun', 't', '63', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M1123684013b5f4c4468280prod4con2&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(135, 'Improving transmembrane protein consensus topology prediction using inter-helical interaction', 'uploadFile/c11e4d0e-7e52-4eba-91ae-c6dafdccd4f4.pdf', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/full_record.do?product=UA&search_mode=GeneralSearch&qid=2&SID=3Ao4eCLI54G6jkD8onm&page=1&doc=1', 115, 115, 49, '2012-12-03 09:34:40', '2012-12-09', '1', 'Biochimica et Biophysica Acta', '2012-11', 'Transmembrane Topology,Consensus prediction Contact', '参见英文', 'Alpha helix transmembrane proteins (αTMPs) represent roughly 30% of all open reading frames (ORFs) in a typical\ngenome and are involved in many critical biological processes. Due to the special physicochemical properties, it is\nhard to crystallize and obtain high resolution structures experimentally, thus, sequence-based topology prediction\nis highly desirable for the study of transmembrane proteins (TMPs), both in structure prediction and function prediction.\nVariousmodel-based topology prediction methods have been developed, but the accuracy of those individual\npredictors remain poor due to the limitation of the methods or the features they used. Thus, the consensus\ntopology predictionmethod becomes practical for high accuracy applications by combining the advances of the individual\npredictors. Here, based on the observation that inter-helical interactions are commonly found within the\ntransmembrane helixes (TMHs) and strongly indicate the existence of them, we present a novel consensus topology\nprediction method for αTMPs, CNTOP, which incorporates four top leading individual topology predictors, and further\nimproves the prediction accuracy by using the predicted inter-helical interactions. The method achieved 87%\nprediction accuracy based on a benchmark dataset and 78% accuracy based on a non-redundant dataset which is\ncomposed of polytopic αTMPs. Ourmethod derives the highest topology accuracy than any other individual predictors\nand consensus predictors, at the same time, the TMHs are more accurately predicted in their length and locations,\nwhere both the false positives (FPs) and the false negatives (FNs) decreased dramatically.', 'WOS:000309081700022', 3.99, 0, '1818', '11', '2679–2686', NULL, '', 2, 'Han Wang,Chao Zhang,Xiaohu Shi,Li Zhang,You Zhou', 't', '62', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/full_record.do?product=UA&search_mode=GeneralSearch&qid=2&SID=3Ao4eCLI54G6jkD8onm&page=1&doc=1'),
(136, 'A novel scale-free network construction method and its application in gene expression profiles simulation', 'uploadFile/f244fb8c-5fbf-431f-9837-3c7b32ff21bd.pdf', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/full_record.do?product=UA&search_mode=GeneralSearch&qid=5&SID=3Ao4eCLI54G6jkD8onm&page=1&doc=1', 115, 115, 49, '2012-12-03 09:38:35', '2012-12-09', '1', 'PROG BIOCHEM BIOPHYS', '2012-06', 'gene expression profiles, scale-free network, reconnection, differential equation, heuristic search algorithm', '参见英文', 'In this paper, a novel scale-free network construction algorithm based on reconnection method was proposed. The\nregulatory node of the new node will be reselected according to the reconnection method. The probability of reconnection depends on\nthe gamma in the power-law distribution model parameters. The constructed network with our algorithm was used for simulating gene\nexpression profiles using differential equation model with two heuristic search algorithms, GA and PSO, and new algorithm GFA to\noptimize the criterion. The candidate old node can be selected as regulatory node based on the number of links the old node already\nhas. The network in the experiment was testified using log-log graph. And the simulated gene expression profiles were also tested with\nthree different well developed algorithms'' software available free from internet by reconstructing the network. PPV and Se of the links\nwere calculated and visualized.', '000305659100012', 0.236, 0, '39', '6', '581-590', NULL, '', 2, 'Zheng M, Huang YC , Shen W, Zhong Y, Wu JN, Liu GX, Zhou Y', 't', '63', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/full_record.do?product=UA&search_mode=GeneralSearch&qid=5&SID=3Ao4eCLI54G6jkD8onm&page=1&doc=1');
