(233, '自适应最小误差阈值分割算法', 'uploadFile/e7ebec1d-a93c-403d-91e7-f88d3e5f8a60.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=MOTO201207012&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJQMVd2NFhNRUNmUjJPT1dhU0xzcHpEVzV6L3kycERGdlQvVHpIMkZ6UkdWUmJRdg==', 273, 273, 45, '2012-12-05 07:29:29', '2012-12-07', '1', '自动化学报', '2012-07', ' 图像分割， 自适应阈值分割，Water flow模型，最小误差法', ' 对二维最小误差法进行三维推广,并结合三维直方图重建和降维思想提出了一种鲁棒的最小误差阈值分割算法.但该方法为全局算法,仅适用于分割均匀光照图像.为提高其自适应性,本文采用Waterflow模型对非均匀光照图像进行背景估计,以此获得原始图像与背景图像的差值图像,达到降低非均匀光照对图像分割造成干扰的目的.为进一步提高分割性能,本文对差值图像采用γ矫正进行增强,然后采用鲁棒最小误差法进行全局分割,从而完成目标提取.最后本文对均匀光照下以及非均匀光照下图像进行了实验,并与一维最小误差法、二维最小误差法、三维直方图重建和降维的Otsu阈值分割算法、灰度波动变换自适应阈值方法以及一种改进的FCM方法在错误分割率和运行时间上进行了对比.实验结果表明,相对于以上方法,本算法的分割性能均有明显提升. ', 'A robust minimum error thresholding method is proposed to combine the three-dimensional (3D) minimum\nerror thresholding scheme based on 2D method with the principle of rebuilding and dimension reduction of the 3D\nhistogram. Considering the global behavior of this approach and its ability to process even illumination images only, a water flow model is used to estimate the background of uneven illumination images for improving adaptability of the proposed method. Then, the difference image between the original image and background can be readily obtained to reduce the interference of uneven illumination during the binarization process. To improve execution performance of\nthe segmentation procedure, gamma correction is employed to enhance image in addition to a global segmentation using\nrobust minimum error thresholding algorithm. Subsequently, image segmentation tests are carried out with even and\nuneven illumination, and then comparison on misclassification error and time expenditure are performed between the\nproposed method and other approaches, i.e., 1D/2D minimum error thresholding, Otsu thresholding algorithm based on 3D histogram rebuilding and dimensionality reduction, adaptive gray wave transformation thresholding scheme, as well as a modified FCM method. The results show that the proposed approach yields better thresholding performance than those methods.\n', '20123615396070', 1.064, 0, '38', '7', '1137-1144', NULL, '', 1.5, '龙建武， 申铉京， 陈海鹏', 't', '62', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=MOTO201207012&dbname=CJFD2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJQMVd2NFhNRUNmUjJPT1dhU0xzcHpEVzV6L3kycERGdlQvVHpIMkZ6UkdWUmJRdg=='),
(234, '结合全局和局部灰度拟合活动轮廓模型的图像分割算法', 'uploadFile/b4cbbeb2-29c3-46f9-ac73-0f40f716cccc.pdf', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY20120315008&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJQMVd2NFhNRUNmUjJPT1dhU0xzcHpEVzV6L3kycERGdlQvVHpIMkZ6UkdWUmJRdg==', 273, 273, 42, '2012-12-05 07:49:15', '2012-12-10', '1', '吉林大学学报工学版', '2012-11', '图像处理技术，图像分割，活动轮廓模型，水平集方法，灰度不均', '针对 LIF 模型对初始轮廓敏感和容易陷入局部极小的缺点，本文提出了一种基于图像区域信息的活动轮廓模型。本模型同时利用图像全局和局部信息来分割图像，其能量泛函由四项组成：局部项、面积项、长度项和惩罚项。局部项将图像局部信息融入到模型中，使该模型能有效分割灰度不均图像；面积项通过引入一个全局指示函数，加快了模型的收敛速度，且能避免陷入局部极小；惩罚项约束水平集函数逼近符号距离函数，使模型无需重新初始化，减少了分割时间。此外，为了实现对图像中感兴趣区域的分割，本文给出了模型的窄带实现方法。实验结果表明：本文模型对初始轮廓的敏感性低，收敛速度快，能准确分割灰度不均的图像，且其窄带实现方法能够实现对图像中感兴趣区域的分割。 ', 'As the LIF model is sensitive to the location of initial curve and is trapped into local minimums easily, an active contour model based on image region information is proposed in this work, which utilizes global and local image information to segment images. This energy functional consists of four terms: local term, area term, length term and penalty term. By incorporating the local image information into the presented model, the images with intensity inhomogeneity can be efficiently segmented. And introducing a global indicating function in the area term can speed up the convergence of the proposed model and can also avoid being trapped into\nlocal minima. In addition, the time-consuming re-initialization can be avoided because the penalty term forces the level set function to be close to a signed distance function. In order to segment regions of interest in an image, narrowband implementation of this model is introduced. The experimental results demonstrate that the proposed model is less sensitive to the location of initial curve, converges more quickly than LIF model, and can segment those images with uneven intensity accurately. Moreover, the narrowband implementation can extract regions of interest in images effectively and correctly.\n', '待检索', 0.473, 0, '42', '6', '1532-1537', NULL, '', 0.25, '申铉京，于凯民，王开业，陈海鹏', 't', '63', 'http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=14&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=JLGY20120315008&dbname=CAPJ2012&DbCode=CJFQ&urlid=&yx=&uid=WEEvREcwSlJHSldTTGJhYlJQMVd2NFhNRUNmUjJPT1dhU0xzcHpEVzV6L3kycERGdlQvVHpIMkZ6UkdWUmJRdg=='),
(235, 'Energy balancing multipath routing protocol in wireless multimedia sensor networks', 'uploadFile/f0803b5c-48c9-41b9-a7ad-02c7c3ec4d60.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b69abd87fM2fe6prod1con2&CID=expertSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=expertSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 273, 273, 47, '2012-12-05 08:05:55', '2012-12-10', '1', 'MEGM 2012', '2012-03', 'Geographical Protocol, Multipath Transmission, Network Lifetime, Wireless Multimedia Sensor Networks', '大量的图像和视频流需要无线多媒体传感器网络（WMSNs的）中要被发送，单一的路径不能满足要求的图像和视频流式传输。多路径路由协议可以增加传输能力，适用于WMSNs。 TPGF是第一多径路由协议，这是适合于WMSNs的。对TPGF进行了深入分析，我们提出了一个能量平衡的多路径路由协议（EBMR）考虑节点的剩余能量和节点和接收器之间的距离。相比TPGF，EBMPR可以更均匀地消耗节点的能量，延长网络的生命周期。仿真结果显示了EBMR的优势。', 'A large amount of image and video streaming need to be transmitted in wireless multimedia sensor networks (WMSNs), and a single path can not meet the requirement of image and video streaming transmission. Multipath routing protocol can increase transmission capability and be appropriate for WMSNs. TPGF is the first multipath routing protocol which is suitable for WMSNs. After TPGF is analyzed deeply, we propose an Energy Balancing Multipath Routing protocol (EBMR) which considers nodes'' residual energy and the distance between the node and the sink. Compared to TPGF, EBMPR can more evenly consume nodes'' energy and prolong the network lifetime. Simulation results show the advantage of EBMR.', '20121114857151', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-03-16', '重庆', 0.25, 'En Yan Sun, Xuan Jing Shen, Hai Peng Chen', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=M6f96419c13b69abd87fM2fe6prod1con2&CID=expertSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=1&database=1&format=expertSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(236, 'A Improved Coverage Model and Deployment Algorithm in Internet of Things', 'uploadFile/95828871-bbd6-473e-8c8b-e1da76ac23d5.pdf', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/summary.do?SID=Z2B6gG6KG551gIHiLkE&product=UA&qid=1&search_mode=GeneralSearch', 273, 273, 49, '2012-12-05 08:09:13', '2012-12-07', '1', 'Information-An International Interdisciplinary Journal', '2012-01', 'Three Dimensions，Particle swarm optimization，Uncertainty，Internet of things', '本文提出了一种改进的三维空间中的物联网覆盖模型。在不确定性范围内使用改进的检测模型和非附加措施。许多传统的覆盖模式只描述平面覆盖问题。然而，改进的模型可以解决在三维空间内的不确定性的覆盖问题，并且可以简化子空间投影。基于模型和实践群优化算法，我们提出了一个三维的调度算法，可以解决在物联网中最大融合覆盖率。实验结果表明，提出的调度算法能够获得满意的融合覆盖率。', ' This paper proposes an improved three-dimensional space coverage model in Internet of Things. The improved sensing model and non-additive measure are used in the uncertainty coverage. Many traditional coverage models only describe plane coverage problem. However, the improved model can solve the uncertainty coverage problems within three dimensions and can be simplified by subspace projection. Based on the model and practice swarm optimization, we propose a three-dimensional deployment algorithm that can solve the maximum fusion coverage rate problem in Internet of things. Experimental result showed that the proposed deployment algorithm could obtain satisfying fusion coverage rate in Internet of Things.', '000301809700042', 0.25, 0, '15', '1', '395-402', NULL, '', 2, '曹斌，申铉京，曹双兰，千庆姬', 't', '63', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/summary.do?SID=Z2B6gG6KG551gIHiLkE&product=UA&qid=1&search_mode=GeneralSearch'),
(237, 'A low energy image compression and transmission in wireless multimedia sensor networks', 'uploadFile/f9c42913-1545-49e8-bb93-d72f4dca5204.pdf', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b69b1b99dM3baprod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=3&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes', 273, 273, 47, '2012-12-05 08:55:43', '2012-12-10', '1', 'CEIS 2011', '2012-01', 'wireless multimedia sensor networks， image compression， JPEG，clustering algorithm，the network lifetime', '无线多媒体传感器网络（WMSNs的）的重点转向标无线传感器网络的网络与多媒体设备，能够检索视频、图片、音频，以及标量传感器数据。然而，传统的图像压缩算法，能量消耗迅速，缩短了网络的生命周期。在本文中，我们详细分析了在WMSNs的JPEG标准和改进的版本。我们提出了一种新的低能量图像压缩算法（LEICA）基于一个感兴趣的领域。 LEICA可以保持兴趣区域的图像质量，并增加整个图像的压缩比。此外，LEICA可以延长网络的生命周期。仿真实验结果显示了LEICA的优势。', 'Wireless Multimedia Sensor networks (WMSNs) have shifted the focus from scalar wireless sensor networks to networks with multimedia devices that are capable to retrieve video, images, audio, as well as scalar sensor data. However, the traditional image compression algorithms that need too much computation can deplete nodes'' energy quickly and shorten the network lifetime. In this paper, we analyze the JPEG standard and improved version in WMSNs in detail. Then we propose a novel Low Energy Image Compression Algorithm (LEICA) that is based on an interest area in WMSNs. LEICA can keep an image quality of an interest area and increase the compression ratio of the whole image. Furthermore, LEICA can prolong the network lifetime. Simulation experiments show the advantages of LEICA. ', '20115214631385', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-08-18', '云南大理', 0.25, 'Sun Enyan，Shen Xuanjing， Chen Haipeng', 't', '62', 'http://www.engineeringvillage.org/controller/servlet/Controller?SEARCHID=1d89255f13b69b1b99dM3baprod1con1&CID=quickSearchDetailedFormat&DOCINDEX=3&database=1&format=quickSearchDetailedFormat&tagscope=&displayPagination=yes'),
(238, 'The Multi-Channel Connection Management based on MOST Network Management', 'uploadFile/6eb8c0b8-659b-4b3a-9f40-6c55a9c681d4.pdf', '无', 3, 3, 47, '2012-12-05 12:21:43', '2012-12-11', '1', '2012 Second International Conference on Electronics, Communications and Control', '2012-10', 'network management，central registry，finite state machine，multi-channel connection management', '为了适应动态变化的面向媒体的系统传输 ＭＯＳＴ 网络环境 提出了一种基于ＭＯＳＴ网络管理的连接管理策略 该策略动态更新中心注册表 管理 ＭＯＳＴ网络中数据源与目的端口 并实现了多同步信道连接的建立 释放与切换等操作 在采用 ＭＯＳＴ５０网络节点搭建的环型网络中 通过 ＭＯＳＴ网络分析器 Ｏ ｐ ｔｏＬ ｙ ｚｅｒ的功能性验证表明 该策略有效提高了 ＭＯＳＴ网络带宽的利用率。', 'Media oriented systems transport (MOST) is the \nmost promising solution for in-vehcile multimedia \napplications. The coupling between physical position and\ndevice function of network nodes, and the single-connection in synchronous channel in actual development, however, limit the flexible application and the available bandwidth resource of MOST network system. This paper proposes an implementation of the network  management descibed the process of network management  through finite state model, and discusses the multi-channel connection management manages the multi-channel connection in network concurrently. Both of them give a solution for the problem in pratice.', '无', 0.88, 0, '', '', '', '2012-10-16', 'China', 0.25, ' 陈筠翰，秦贵和，南　洋', 't', '63', '无'),
(239, 'Sparse Tensor Discriminant Color Space for Face Verification', 'uploadFile/a513f7b0-3663-4f6d-ac37-1b7bb62859fd.pdf', '没有', 223, 223, 49, '2012-12-05 13:36:00', '2012-12-07', '1', 'IEEE Transactions on Neural Networks and Learning Systems', '2012-06', 'Color images,discriminant information,face recognition,sparse representation,tensor subspace', '无', 'As one of the fundamental features, color provides useful information and plays an important role for face\nrecognition. Generally, the choice of a color space is different for different visual tasks. How can a color space be\nsought for the specific face recognition problem? To address this problem, we propose a sparse tensor discriminant\ncolor space (STDCS) model that represents a color image as a third-order tensor in this paper. The model cannot\nonly keep the underlying spatial structure of color images but also enhance robustness and give intuitionistic or\nsemantic interpretation. STDCS transforms the eigenvalue problem to a series of regression problems. Then one\nspare color space transformation matrix and two sparse discriminant projection matrices are obtained by applying\nlasso or elastic net on the regression problems. The experiments on three color face databases, AR, Georgia Tech,\nand Labeled Faces in the Wild face databases, show that both the performance and the robustness of the proposed\nmethod outperform those of the state-of-the-art TDCS model.', '975PB', 2, 0, '23', '6', '876-888', NULL, '', 2, '2.	Su-Jing Wang, Jian Yang, Member, IEEE, Ming-Fang Sun, Xu-Jun Peng, Ming-Ming Sun, and Chun-Guang Zhou', 't', '62', '没有'),
(240, 'A global k-modes algorithm for clustering categorical data. Chinese Journal of Electronics', 'uploadFile/ca7e4b9b-eb53-4335-ab2d-0dcb692da994.pdf', '无', 223, 220, 49, '2012-12-05 13:39:59', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Bai, T (Bai Tian); Kulikowski, CA (Kulikowski, C. A.); Gong, LG (Gong Leiguang); Yang, B (Yang Bin);', '2012-06', 'Categorical data，Clustering，Data mining，K-modes algorithm', '无', 'In this paper, a new Global k-modes (GKM) algorithm is proposed for clustering categorical data. The new\nmethod randomly selects a sufficiently large number of initial modes to account for the global distribution of the\ndata set, and then progressively eliminates the redundant modes using an iterative optimization process with an\nelimination criterion function. Systematic experiments were carried out with data from the UCI Machine learning\nrepository. The results and a comparative evaluation show a high performance and consistency of the proposed\nmethod, which achieves significant improvement compared to other well-known k-modes-type algorithms in terms\nof clustering accuracy.', '976WS', 1, 0, '21', '3', '460-465', NULL, '', 1.5, 'Bai, T (Bai Tian); Kulikowski, CA (Kulikowski, C. A.); Gong, LG (Gong Leiguang); Yang, B (Yang Bin);', 't', '63', '无'),
(241, 'A fuzzy k-prototype clustering algorithm for mixed numeric and categorical data', 'uploadFile/df5514d7-b5df-4c1c-9919-92492b579875.pdf', ' ', 223, 224, 49, '2012-12-05 13:43:52', '2012-12-07', '1', 'Knowledge-Based Systems', '2012-06', 'Fuzzy clustering; Data mining; Mixed data; Dissimilarity measure; Attribute significance', ' ', 'In many applications, data objects are described by both numeric and categorical features. The k-prototype\nalgorithm is one of the most important algorithms for clustering this type of data. However, this method performs\nhard partition, which may lead to misclassification for the data objects in the boundaries of regions, and the\ndissimilarity measure only uses the user-given parameter for adjusting the significance of attribute. In this paper,\nfirst, we combine mean and fuzzy centroid to represent the prototype of a cluster, and employ a new measure based\non co-occurrence of values to evaluate the dissimilarity between data objects and prototypes of clusters. This\nmeasure also takes into account the significance of different attributes towards the clustering process. Then we\npresent our algorithm for clustering mixed data. Finally, the performance of the proposed method is demonstrated by\na series of experiments on four real world datasets in comparison with that of traditional clustering algorithms. (C)\n2012 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.', '932EW', 2, 0, '30', ' ', '129-135', NULL, '', 2, 'Ji, JC (Ji, Jinchao); Pang, W (Pang, Wei); Zhou, CG (Zhou, Chunguang); Han, X (Han, Xiao); Wang, Z', 't', '62', ' '),
(242, '一种基于WordNet的短文本语义相似算法', 'uploadFile/2c275192-b70e-4ee7-bf57-829f86b500db.pdf', '  00', 223, 226, 45, '2012-12-05 13:58:20', '2012-12-10', '1', '电子学报', '2012-07', 'semantic, similarity of shorttext, wordnet ,corpus based metho', ' ', 'abstract', '0000', 0, 0, '40', '3', '617-620', NULL, '', 1.5, '翟延冬，周春光，王康平', 't', '63', '  00'),
(243, 'Load Balancing Parallel Hash Join Algorithm Based on Shared Cached CMP', 'uploadFile/5ee8f527-cd06-4c46-b0ea-075756246224.pdf', 'http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/asp/asl/2012/00000005/00000002/art00058', 39, 33, 40, '2012-12-05 14:51:17', '2012-12-11', '1', 'Advanced Sciences Letters', '2012-02', 'CHIP MULTI-PROCESSOR,PARALLEL QUERY PROCESSING, QUERY OPTIMIZATION ', '-', 'Chip Multi-Processor (CMP) presents new opportunities for improving database performance on large queries. Because various resources are shared by many threads, such as L2-Cache, multiprocessors system and simultaneous multithreading are inherently different from CMP system. Based on Chip Multi-Processor (CMP), this paper explores multithreaded hash join execution optimization framework. A major problem of hash join algorithm is that if the hash table can not fit into the cache, each access to the hash table is likely to cause one cache thrashing due to its random nature. To resolve this problem, we designed a reusable triangular buffering structure such that the partitioning granularity is smaller than the cache capacity. Furthermore, in order to reduce cache access conflict in the multithreaded join phase, we optimized the partitioning granularity in accordance with the number of threads. Besides, to address the issue of imbalance of thread''s workload, we proposed a novel method to optimize the workload assignment among threads. Our theoretical analysis and empirical evaluation show that the proposed algorithm could impressively improve in the performance of hash join operation. ', '0', 0, 0, '5', '2', '749-754', NULL, '', 0.25, 'Chen, Yongheng; Zuo, Wanli; Yuan, Man; He, Fenglin; Chen, Kerui', 't', '62', 'http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/asp/asl/2012/00000005/00000002/art00058'),
(244, 'User experience evaluation of Google search for obtaining medical knowledge: a case study', 'uploadFile/39dbe64f-e0ce-489c-9dca-372423fa576c.pdf', 'http://inderscience.metapress.com/content/u3676hg57202kh18/', 119, 286, 49, '2012-12-05 16:50:01', '2012-12-07', '1', 'INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF DATA MINING AND BIOINFORMATICS', '2012-02', 'internet search,  user experience evaluation, Google, medical information', '越来越多的人用类似Google这样的互联网搜索引擎来了解一些疾病的情况和可能的治疗方法。我们用走廊测试的方法来评价Google提供给用户所需的医药信息的能力。作为样例，我们用Google来搜索“Breat Cancer”，得到一份搜索结果。有6个志愿受测用户依照他们的经验来给这份搜索结果所提供的前500个网页打分。我们的研究结果显示Google所提供的前50个搜索结果通常对用户来说是很有用的，可是有些对用户所需帮助很大的网页却会被遗落在排名200位之后，不易被用户所发现。作为Google一类的搜索引擎来说，对于搜索结果的重新排序，一般基于用户对网页点击率，对于那些排名超过200的网页来说，很少有机会被普通用户所点击查看。这样，那些对于用户所需比较有用的网页自然也很少有机会来提高它们的点击率和排名。综上所述，Google对于用户使用来搜索获得所需的医药信息的表现是令人满意和推荐的，只是在搜索的灵敏度方面还有较大的改进空间。', 'More and more people use Internet search engines, especially Google, to learn diseases and possible treatments. We conducted a hallway testing to evaluate the effectiveness of Google in obtaining medical information. We searched “Breast Cancer” using Google. Six volunteers scored their experience for each of the top 500 websites and the result was evaluated by a physician. Our study shows that 50 hits of Google often help lay users in getting medical information, but some highly useful websites may be buried beyond top 200. As Google re-ranks websites based on their hits and users rarely visit websites ranking beyond top 200, these helpful websites have little chance to improve their rankings. In conclusion, the specificity of using Google in searching for medical information is satisfactory while the sensitivity of the search has significant room for improvement. ', 'WOS:000299296400003', 0.9, 1, '5', '6', '626-639', NULL, '', 2, 'LIUPU WANG，JUEXIN WANG，MICHAEL WANG，YANCHUN LIANG，DONG XU', 't', '63', 'http://inderscience.metapress.com/content/u3676hg57202kh18/'),
(245, 'Using Internet Search Engines to Obtain Medical Information: A Comparative Study', 'uploadFile/62019d32-8fdc-40f0-a611-854aaaffcba0.pdf', 'http://www.jmir.org/2012/3/e74/', 119, 286, 49, '2012-12-05 17:09:38', '2012-12-07', '1', 'JOURNAL OF MEDICAL INTERNET RESEARCH', '2012-05', 'Internet search; page rank; Google, Yahoo!, Bing, Ask.com; medical information; health information seeking', '研究背景：互联网已经成为人们获取健康和医学信息最为重要的途径之一。它往往是人们查询有关疾病和药物基础知识的首选方式，以Google、Yahoo！、Bing和Ask.com为代表的各种主流搜索引擎在提供和评估医学信息方面可以起到重要的作用。\n研究目的：该文研究的目的是针对当下主流的网络搜索引擎，对其在向普通用户提供医学健康信息方面的表现做可用性测试，进行用户体验评估。就软件工程的技术和行业化标准而言，这对于搜索引擎的评估是具有重要意义的。\n研究方法：本次研究主要包括四个部分。首先，我们分别用Google、Yahoo！、Bing和Ask.com这四种搜索引擎搜索关键字“Breast Cancer”，获取前200个搜索结果组成4个搜索结果样本组。并对这4组搜索结果进行组内和组间的相似性分析。然后，将所有的搜索结果按照网页内容进行分类，进行组内和组间的比较分析。随后，我们邀请受测用户依次浏览所有的搜索结果，按照其所提供的信息的有用程度打分，最低为0分，最高为10分，以医学专家给出的业内公认对于了解Breast Cancer的相关知识最有帮助的一些网站作为10分的标准。记录所有打分结果，按照打分结果重新对4组搜索结果重新排序。另一方面,对这4组搜索结果每个网页的首页及其次级链接的子页所提供的文字内容做关键词搜索，记录所命中的关键词的个数和类别。关键词取自从SNOMED CT中查询到的”Breast Cancer”的同义词。按照关键词的搜索结果重新对4组搜索结果重新排序。对以上所得到的原搜索结果排序、人工评价打分结果排序，以及关键词搜索结果排序等三个网站排序结果进行比较分析。\n研究结果：医学专家推荐的对于普通用户了解乳腺癌相关信息和知识很有帮助价值的网站和网页，可以被Google、Yahoo!、Bing和Ask.com这4种搜索引擎较为准确地搜索到，并在搜索结果列表前30位之内。各搜索结果样本组中搜索结果有效性分析结果显示，Google引擎的搜索结果有效性最高，其后依次是Bing、Ask.com和Yahoo！多搜索引擎结果的相似性分析结果显示，4种搜索引擎的搜索结果中有半数以上的结果之间是相互重复或者相似的。其中，只有Google的结果样本相互之间无一重复，其搜索结果的相似性程度也最低。搜索结果样本网页内容分类统计的结果显示，不同搜索引擎对不同网页内容类型的侧重各有不同。受测用户对于Bing搜索引擎提供的医学健康信息相关的搜索结果的满意度最高，其次是Yahoo!，第三是Google，最后的是Ask.com搜索结果样本网页内容信息量的计算结果显示，4种主流搜索引擎的搜索结果中排名靠前的样本网页有很多都是富含有用信息的。\n研究结论：总体而言，Google、Yahoo!、Bing和Ask.com这4种主流搜索引擎对于互联网信息搜索用户获取所需的医学健康信息的表现是令人满意和推荐的。使用互联网搜索引擎来获取需要的医学健康知识和信息，对于互联网用户来说是一种十分有效的方法。只是现有的对搜索结果的排序准确性和各种类型信息的兼顾与平衡方面，仍然有一些需要更进一步完善和改进的空间。我们建议搜索引擎用户在医学信息检索过程中，选择使用不同的搜索引擎来搜索不同类型的医学健康知识和信息。', 'Background: The Internet has become one of the most important means to obtain health and medical information. It is often the first step in checking for basic information about a disease and its treatment. The search results are often useful to general users. Various search engines such as Google, Yahoo!, Bing, and Ask.com can play an important role in obtaining medical information for both medical professionals and lay people. However, the usability and effectiveness of various search engines for medical information have not been comprehensively compared and evaluated.\nObjective: To compare major Internet search engines in their usability of obtaining medical and health information.\nMethods: We applied usability testing as a software engineering technique and a standard industry practice to compare the four major search engines (Google, Yahoo!, Bing, and Ask.com) in obtaining health and medical information. For this purpose, we searched the keyword breast cancer in Google, Yahoo!, Bing, and Ask.com and saved the results of the top 200 links from each search engine. We combined nonredundant links from the four search engines and gave them to volunteer users in an alphabetical order. The volunteer users evaluated the websites and scored each website from 0 to 10 (lowest to highest) based on the usefulness of the content relevant to breast cancer. A medical expert identified six well-known websites related to breast cancer in advance as standards. We also used five keywords associated with breast cancer defined in the latest release of Systematized Nomenclature of Medicine-Clinical Terms (SNOMED CT) and analyzed their occurrence in the websites.\nResults: Each search engine provided rich information related to breast cancer in the search results. All six standard websites were among the top 30 in search results of all four search engines. Google had the best search validity (in terms of whether a website could be opened), followed by Bing, Ask.com, and Yahoo!. The search results highly overlapped between the search engines, and the overlap between any two search engines was about half or more. On the other hand, each search engine emphasized various types of content differently. In terms of user satisfaction analysis, volunteer users scored Bing the highest for its usefulness, followed by Yahoo!, Google, and Ask.com.\nConclusions: Google, Yahoo!, Bing, and Ask.com are by and large effective search engines for helping lay users get health and medical information. Nevertheless, the current ranking methods have some pitfalls and there is room for improvement to help users get more accurate and useful information. We suggest that search engine users explore multiple search engines to search different types of health information and medical knowledge for their own needs and get a professional consultation if necessary.', 'WOS:000305797300029', 4.7, 0, '14', '3', '370-388', NULL, '', 2, 'LIUPU WANG, JUEXIN WANG, MICHAEL WANG, YONG LI, YANCHUN LIANG, DONG XU', 't', '62', 'http://www.jmir.org/2012/3/e74/'),
(246, 'Improved defense against domain name server man-in-the-middle spoofing', 'uploadFile/53df4444-ce8b-4214-9a1f-f5b4907d1fe6.pdf', 'http://www.aspbs.com/ctn/', 60, 60, 49, '2012-12-06 00:50:12', '2012-12-11', '1', 'Journal of Computational and Theoretical Nanoscience', '2012-10', ' DNS, Man-in-the-middle, Spoofing attack, Defence, Na?ve Bayes classifier', '见英文', 'The Domain Name System, or DNS, is an important facility in the Internet. But for some reasons, DNS interaction is quite vulnerable to a kind of man-in-the-middle (MITM) spoofing attack. This paper illustrates the MITM spoofing attack and proposes a type of defense technique employing Naive Bayes (NB) Classifier. Considering three types of individual factors, then illustrates, analyzes and evaluates their performances. The 3-factor NB technique achieves the best performance with an average identifying ratio of 99.7875%. What’s more, we provide a proposal on taking balance of precision and time consumption accordingly. In all, the presented NB technique is quite helpful in defense against DNS MITM spoofing attack.', 'SCI期刊待检索', 0.912, 0, '9', '10', '1750-1756', NULL, '', 2, 'Kuo Zhao, Xiaolong Bai, Feng Wang, Yuyu Sun, Liang Hu', 't', '63', 'http://www.aspbs.com/ctn/'),
(247, 'The design and implementation of composite Collaborative Filtering algorithm for personalized recommendation', 'uploadFile/41a43a61-bdf3-4877-9d1f-ed12bde8cb5b.pdf', 'http://ojs.academypublisher.com/index.php/jsw/article/view/jsw070920402045/5514', 60, 60, 41, '2012-12-06 01:03:12', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Journal of Software', '2012-09', 'composite collaborative filtering algorithm; none of user starting; data sparsity; top-M.', '见下面', 'A composite collaborative filtering algorithm for personalized recommend will be presented to solve the\noriginal Collaborative Filtering algorithm problem\nincluding“None of User Starting ”and “Data Sparsity”,\nand the Spearman rank correlation coefficient will be used as a main correlation coefficient. Top-M commended is going to be used to get the final results in this paper. At last, we will validate that this algorithm is superior to the algorithm of collaborative filtering based on user and the algorithm of collaborative filtering based on item.', '20124215583189', 0, 0, '7', '9', '2040-2045', NULL, '', 2, 'Liang Hu, Wenbo Wang, Feng Wang, Xiaolu Zhang, Kuo Zhao', 't', '62', 'http://ojs.academypublisher.com/index.php/jsw/article/view/jsw070920402045/5514'),
(248, 'Research on the architecture model of volatile data forensics', 'uploadFile/64f4dd59-e323-463c-8b95-7109a085eab7.pdf', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877705812006637', 60, 60, 41, '2012-12-06 01:08:15', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Procedia Engineering', '2012-03', 'Computer forensic; Digital forensic; Volatile data; Forensic model; Live forensic; Memory forensic', '见下面', 'This paper proposed a new architecture model of volatile data forensic. The model applied to all the volatile data\nsources is a general model. It can rebuild the evidence data fragment to chains of evidence which contains the\nbehavior characteristics, so as to assist investigators to do case analysis. With the accumulated experience, the model can help judicial officers to intelligently analyze the same type of computer crimes, and based on currently available information to predict the impending crimes.', '20121214883299', 0, 0, '29', '2012', '4254-4258', NULL, '', 0.25, 'Liang Hu, XiaoLu Zhang, Feng Wang, WenBo Wang, Kuo Zhao', 't', '63', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877705812006637'),
(249, 'An efficient AC algorithm with GPU', 'uploadFile/0627b01a-8204-484e-9b69-ee724e288cec.pdf', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877705812006625', 60, 60, 41, '2012-12-06 01:11:34', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Procedia Engineering', '2012-03', 'Pattern matching; CPU; AC', '见下面', 'Pattern matching algorithm is the basis of information biology as well as information retrieval research field. As far as the current computing capability of CPU is concerned, it may hardly satisfy the demand in terms of system realtime when faced by a large amount of data. Due to the enormous computing potential of GPU, various efforts have been made for the computing task migration to GPU with given application programs. In this paper, we present an AC Multi-pattern matching algorithm based on GPU with the parallelization of traditional algorithm based on CPU, and the matching efficiency may be significantly improved due to the high performance parallel processing capability of GPU. Experimental results show our proposed scheme achieved a better speed-up compared to the original one.', '20121214883298', 0, 0, '29', '2012', '4249-4253', NULL, '', 0.25, 'Liang Hu, Zhen Wei, Feng Wang, Xiaolu Zhang, Kuo Zhao', 't', '62', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877705812006625'),
(250, 'A heuristic skipping rules algorithm on tableau algorithm', 'uploadFile/672d2f48-b398-4d47-a16b-a2fdc00dd311.pdf', 'http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/articleDetails.jsp?arnumber=6188151', 60, 60, 47, '2012-12-06 01:16:47', '2012-12-10', '1', '2012 International Conference on Computer Science and Electronics Engineering', '2012-03', 'ontology reasoning; description logic; tableau', '见下面', 'Ontology description can use Description Logic(DL)\nlanguage, so DL’s reasoning service can be used in ontology reasoning. In each kind DL, there is a corresponding tableau algorithm to do the reasoning process. There are some sophisticated software to do DL reasoning, they using tree with conflict to decide whether a problem can be using satisfiability to\nsolve. There are a lot of optimization methods to optimize the reasoning service, their attention on the tree structure with conflict. We propose a new algorithm, Heuristic Skipping Rules Algorithm(HSRA), to simply the rule set called by tableau algorithms, and experimentally proved the effectiveness of the HSRA.', '20122115034367', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-03-25', '杭州', 0.25, 'He Jinshan, Hu Liang, Zhao Kuo, Du Zhanwei', 't', '63', 'http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/articleDetails.jsp?arnumber=6188151'),
(251, 'Review of cyber-physical system architecture', 'uploadFile/cc93c997-dc9e-436c-901e-a635db6c1f3b.pdf', 'http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/stamp/stamp.jsp?tp=&arnumber=6196100', 60, 60, 47, '2012-12-06 01:22:13', '2012-12-10', '1', '2012 15th IEEE International Symposium on Object/Component/Service-Oriented Real-Time Distributed Computing Workshops', '2012-04', 'Cyber-Physical Systems; CPS architecture;', '见下面', 'With the goal of accomplish the ubiquitous intelligence in social life, Cyber-Physical Systems (CPS) are getting growing attentions of researchers and engineers. However, the complexity of computing and physical dynamics bring a lot of challenges in the development of CPS, such as integration of heterogeneous physical devices, system verification, security assurance, and so on. A general or unified architecture plays an important part in the process of CPS design. In this paper, we review the current and previous works of CPS architecture, and introduce the main challenges and techniques of architecture development : real-time control, security assurance, integration mechanism. Then we propose a general CPS architecture based on Service-Oriented Architecture (SOA), the main advantage of this proposed architecture is the integration flexibility of services and components. At the end, we introduce the typical applications of CPS, and suggest the future research areas.', '20122215073639', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-04-21', '深恨', 0.25, 'Liang Hu, Nannan Xie, Zhejun Kuang, Kuo Zhao', 't', '62', 'http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/stamp/stamp.jsp?tp=&arnumber=6196100'),
(252, 'A novel cooperative particle swarm optimizer with statistical variable interdependence learning', 'uploadFile/7c262817-6404-48a9-bcaf-b21e28fb0ad0.PDF', ' ', 120, 113, 49, '2012-12-06 01:28:41', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Information Sciences', '2012-01', 'Numerical optimization, Cooperative optimization, Variable interdependence, Problem decomposition', ' ', 'Cooperative optimization algorithms, such as the cooperative coevolutionary genetic algorithm(CCGA) and the cooperative particle swarm optimization (CPSO) algorithm, have already been used with success to solve many optimization problems. One of the most important issues in cooperative optimization algorithms is the task of decomposition. Decomposition decision regarding variable interdependencies plays a significant role in the algorithm’s performance. Algorithms that do not consider variable interdependencies often lose their effectiveness and advantages when applied to solve nonseparable problems.\nIn this paper, we propose a cooperative particle swarm optimizer with statistical variable interdependence learning (CPSO-SL). A statistical model is proposed to explore the interdependencies among variables. With these interdependencies, the algorithm partitions large scale problems into overlapping small scale subproblems. Moreover, a CPSO framework is proposed to optimize the subproblems cooperatively. Finally, theoretical analysis is presented for further understanding of the proposed CPSO-SL. Simulated experiments were conducted on 10 classical benchmarks, 10 rotated classical benchmarks, and 10 CEC2005 benchmarks. The results demonstrate the performance of CPSO-SL in solving both separable and nonseparable problems, as compared with the performance of other recent cooperative optimization algorithms.', '000', 2.833, 0, '186', '1', '20-39', NULL, '', 2, 'Sun Liang, Yoshida Shinichi, Cheng Xiaochun, Liang Yanchun', 't', '63', ' '),
(253, 'Biological process identification based on gene overlapping grouping algorithm', 'uploadFile/d85eacb4-b0f1-4a8b-aabf-b557dc0bb7b8.pdf', '   ', 117, 113, 47, '2012-12-06 01:30:50', '2012-12-10', '1', '2012 6th International Conference on Bioinformatics and Biomedical Engineering (iCBBE)', '2012-12', 'Gene cluster, Gene community overlapping,', '基于基因重叠分组算法的生物过程识别.', 'Identifying the gene sets involved in the same\nfunctional groups or biological pathway is an important\nresearch topic in computational biology. A large number of\nclustering methods have been proposed and used for this\npurpose. However, majority of methods lack of study on the\noverlapping relations between gene functional groups. It is\ncommon that the same gene is involved in different biological\npathways simultaneously. In this paper, we find that allowing\ngene groups to have overlap can significantly improve\nclustering algorithm for gene function study, which is\nconsistent with the real biological process. It is found that the overlapping genes often have more activities involved in\nbiological process than other genes.', '000', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2012-05-17', '上海', 0.25, '李丹,李瑛,邹淑雪,梁艳春,许东', 't', '62', '   '),
(254, ' Multi-BPexpert system for fault diagnosis of power system', 'uploadFile/8dbe11fc-f44a-4183-89d9-a1239a9ec736.pdf', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0952197612000851', 120, 120, 49, '2012-12-06 01:39:25', '2012-12-11', '1', 'Engineering ApplicationsofArtificialIntelligence', '2012-12', 'Power system, Expert system, Multi-BP networks', ' ', 'Fault diagnosis and assessment is a crucial and difficult problem for power system. Back propagation neural network expert system (BPES) is an often used method in fault diagnosis. However, with the layer number’s increasing, BPES becomes time consuming and even hard to converge. To solve this problem, we divide the whole networks into many sub-BP groups within a short depth and then propose a novel Multi-BP expert system (MBPES) based method for power system fault diagnosis. We use two real power system data sets to test the effectiveness of MBPES. Experimental results show that MBPES obtains higher accuracy than two commonly used methods.', '000', 1.665, 0, '00', '00', '00', NULL, '', 2, 'Ma DY, Liang YC, Zhao XS, Guan RC and Shi XH', 't', '63', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0952197612000851'),
(255, ' Design of stack based on hairpin structure in DNA computer', 'uploadFile/8487c731-68bf-41a0-ae24-560837f90f44.pdf', ' http://asmedl.org/ebooks/asme/asme_press/859926/859926_paper27', 120, 113, 46, '2012-12-06 01:48:28', '2012-12-11', '1', ' International Conference on Computer and Computer Intelligence (ICCCI 2011)', '2012-12', 'DNA Computer ', ' ', 'Data structure is very important for computer science. Since DNA computing appeared, many researchers have use this computing paradigms to solve problems, especially NP-hard problems because of its advantages of parallelism and mass storage. In order to be used in practice, DNA computer need to availably organize data as electronic computer. Stack is a data structure widely used in practice. In this paper, a method for data storage of stack based on hairpin structure in DNA computer is described. And data operation method is demonstrated. The idea of this paper is feasible to solve data organization problem for DNA computer so that it can help DNA computer develop for practical application.', '0', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-12-02', 'Bangkok, Thailand', 0.25, 'Hong Zheng, Zhili Pei, Qing’an Yao, Qinghu Wang, Yanchun Liang', 't', '62', ' http://asmedl.org/ebooks/asme/asme_press/859926/859926_paper27'),
(256, 'DNA algorithm based on k-armed molecule and sticker model for shortest path problem', 'uploadFile/db2b6dea-c4cd-4c7d-bdb8-707a8e4135b7.pdf', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/summary.do?SID=1COOioFMbJf3I3dCNh%40&product=UA&qid=5&search_mode=GeneralSearch', 120, 113, 47, '2012-12-06 01:54:48', '2012-12-10', '1', 'the 2nd International Congress on Computer Applications and Computational Science', '2012-12', 'DNA computing; k-armed molecule; sticker model; shortest path problem ', ' ', 'DNA computing is a computing paradigm based on biochemical reactions by using DNA molecule. Because of its advantages, such as mass storage and parallelism, it has been used to solve many complex problems. Shortest path problem is a frequently used problem in practical application. In this paper, a DNA algorithm based on k-armd molecule and sticker model to solve shortest path problem for weighted graph is proposed. The encoding method for the vertex, edges and weights is described in detail. This method shorten the length of the DNA strands for the weight code and may decrease the error during the biochemical reaction in a certain degree. The solving process for shortest path problem is also described in this paper. ', 'BCI36 ', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-11-15', 'tUBAN, INDONESIA ', 0.25, 'Hong Zheng, Zhili Pei, Qing’an Yao, Qinghu Wang, Yanchun Liang', 't', '63', 'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/summary.do?SID=1COOioFMbJf3I3dCNh%40&product=UA&qid=5&search_mode=GeneralSearch'),
(257, 'Support vector description of clusters for image annotation', 'uploadFile/86d1941e-3901-4c70-9ff2-e71d4cf29774.pdf', ' ', 120, 113, 46, '2012-12-06 02:01:07', '2012-12-11', '1', 'International Workshop on Advanced Computational Intelligence and Intelligent Informatics', '2012-12', 'Content Based Image Retrieval, Support Vector Clustering, Support Vector Description, Image Annotation, Computer Vision', ' ', 'Image annotation is a challenging problem\ndue to the rapid growing of real world image archives.\nIn this paper, we propose a novel approach to the solv-\ning of this problem based on a variant of the support\nvector clustering (SVC) algorithm, i.e., the support\nvector description of clusters. The system has two ma-\njor components, the training process and the annotat-\ning process. In the training process, clusters of im-\nage manually annotated by descriptive words are used\nas training instances. Each cluster is described by a\none-cluster SVC model. The proposed model can ex-\nploit the advantage of SVC for its ability to delineate\ncluster boundaries of arbitrary shape. Moreover, the\ntraining process of the one-cluster SVC model is for-\nmulated as the process of building density estimator\nfor underlying distribution of the cluster. In the an-\nnotating process, for a test image, the probability of\nthis instance being generated by each model is com-\nputed. And then the relevant words are selected based\non the obtained probabilities. Simulated experiments\nwere conducted on the Corel60k data set. The results\ndemonstrate the performance of the proposed algo-\nrithm, compared with the performance of other algo-\nrithms.', '0', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2011-11-19', 'Suzhou, China', 0.25, 'Sun L, Yoshida S, Liang YC', 't', '62', ' '),
(258, 'A Novel Fuzzy K-Mean Algorithm With Fuzzy Centroid For Clustering Mixed Numeric And Categorical Data', 'uploadFile/ed0574c7-74cc-4472-9c42-28bcc6fae93a.pdf', ' ', 224, 224, 41, '2012-12-06 02:11:10', '2012-12-10', '1', 'Advances in information sciences and service sciences', '2012-04', 'Fuzzy Clustering, Data Mining, Mixed Data, Dissimilarity Measure', ' ', 'Most of the fuzzy c-mean type algorithms have the problem that all data objects tend to influence all \nclusters. In 2003, Klawonn and Hoppner proposed a new fuzzy c-mean algorithm to overcome this \nproblem. However, their method is only designed for numeric data, and in many applications data \nobjects are usually described by both numeric and categorical attributes. In this paper, we extends \ntheir method to mixed data. In our method, we first present a new representation for the center of a \ncluster with mixed numeric and categorical attributes, and propose a new measure to evaluate the \ndissimilarity between data objects and centers of clusters. Then we present our algorithm for clustering \nmixed data. The performance of proposed method is demonstrated by a series of experiments on two \nreal datasets in comparison with that of traditional clustering algorithms.', '20121814988344', 0, 2, '4', '7', '256-264', NULL, '', 2, 'Ji, Jinchao  Zhou, Chunguang; Bai, Tian; Zhao, Jian; Wang, Zhe', 't', '63', ' ');
