(388, '基于能耗转移与数据作用力的WSN 节能修正算法', 'uploadFile/c239701a-fe06-49e3-b0c4-e080373bbda9.pdf', '0', 158, 158, 42, '2012-12-13 15:35:55', '2012-12-13', '1', '吉林大学学报工学版', '2012-09', '计算机系统结构,无线传感器网络,节能,关系曲线分析,数据作用力', '针对无线传感器网络能量受限的问题，提出通过判断传感器节点状态阈值来改变其状态的方式，将能耗最大路径的能耗分散到其他能耗相对较少的路径上，以便增加网络整体生命周期的节能修正算法。通过实验分析无线\n网络传感器路由算法得到传感器节点数据传递量与发生相应数据传递量的节点数量的概率之间的关系曲线，并给出了影响关系曲线的参数，同时分析了关系曲线的特征，获得网络中能耗最多节点的分布特点，根据该点，确定节能修正算法中的阈值；由于该算法本身消耗能量，给出数据作用力的概念，应用该概念降低算法自身的能耗，实验验证该算法降低了无线传感器网络能耗，增加了网络生命周期，并对实验结果做了分析。', 'An energy-efficient amendatory algorithm was proposed to save limited energy in WSN. Sensor node changed its status bythe threshold of its energy condition; therefore, the energy consumption in the path with the sensor node with most energyconsumption could be transferred to other paths in order to decrease the whole energy consumption of the network. Through experiments and analysis the curve of the relationship between the probability of nodes’ amount and the amount of data transmission was obtained; the factors that affect this curve were analyzed; the curve features and the threshold mentioned above were found.\nNevertheless, because of the energy consumption of the algorithm itself, the concept of data gravitation was proposed to reduce the\nenergy consumption. The algorithm is demonstrated to be energy efficient, and experiments show that the lifecycles of the networks\nhave been increased successfully.', '20124415623003 (JA)', 0, 0, '2012', '1', '1237-1242', NULL, '', 0.25, '刘壮，房至一，张春飞， 陈琳，赵阳', 't', '63', '0'),
(389, 'A New Range-Free Localization Algorithm Based on Annulus Intersection and Grid Scan in Wireless Sensor Networks', 'uploadFile/d14acdf6-5a68-4286-8ec7-a009019c1d61.pdf', '0', 158, 158, 41, '2012-12-13 15:40:15', '2012-12-13', '1', '             Journal of Information and Computational Science', '2012-04', 'WSN,Node Localization,Annulus Intersection,Grid Scan,Localization Accuracy', '无', 'Aiming at enhancing the localization accuracy of wireless sensor networks, a new localization algorithm\nis presented in this article based on annulus intersection and grid scan (AIGS). Simulation experiments\nhave been performed to compare the AIGS algorithm with some range-free localization algorithm such\nas the centroid algorithm, the DV-hop algorithm, the APIT algorithm, the APIT-T algorithm and so on.\nIt shows that the AIGS algorithm has better localization accuracy than these localization algorithms\nwithout increasing the cost of communication and computation. Experiments have also been done\nto evaluate the effects of two key parameters on the AIGS algorithm. Through analysis about the\ncomparisons between the AIGS algorithm and other range-free localization algorithms, and the conditions\nof itself, it is concluded that the AIGS algorithm can effectively carry out the localization of wireless\nsensor networks.', '20121614955574. （JA）', 0, 0, '2012:9', '4', '831-841', NULL, '', 2, 'Zhuang Liu,Zhiyi Fang,Naiji Ren,Yang Zhao', 't', '62', '0'),
(390, 'A New Localization Algorithm in Wireless sensor networks Based on Improved Genetic Algorithm by Control on Adrenaline Levels', 'uploadFile/05916779-740d-44db-bcd4-c30ea68fdb7a.pdf', '0', 158, 158, 41, '2012-12-13 15:43:40', '2012-12-13', '1', 'Journal of Digital Information Management', '2012-02', 'wireless sensor networks, localization accuracy, control on adrenaline levels, Genetic Algorithm', '无', 'In this paper, a new method is proposed to improve genetic algorithm (GA) based on control on adrenaline levels and a new localization algorithm is designed based on the new method to increase the accuracy of the localization in wireless sensor networks (WSN). We choose the classical localization algorithm, Centroid Algorithm, and perform experiments to demonstrate the localization accuracy of the new algorithm. The result\nshows that it is better than before by using the new algorithm we proposed and it can optimize the localizationalgorithm in WSN.', ' 20121014830846.（JA）', 0, 0, '1', '10', '50-54', NULL, '', 2, 'Liu Zhuang, Fang Zhiyi.', 't', '63', '0'),
(391, 'GPU-Based Research of Highly Efficient Ray Tracing', 'uploadFile/ba16a79f-0de9-4cba-b357-6bf1dfd8c04e.pdf', '0', 158, 158, 40, '2012-12-13 15:49:03', '2012-12-13', '1', 'Advances in Information Sciences and Service Sciences', '2012-01', 'GPU, Streaming programming model Ray tracing, Rasterization', '无', 'By further study of GPU architecture and GPU stream programming model. In this paper, uniform grid acceleration structure implements on the GPU stream programming model of the ray tracing. It has a lot of ray intersection calculations in the whole rendering process, reducing the efficiency of the whole scene rendering. Rendering without compromising the quality of the premise, put forward that use hardware accelerated Z-buffer to determine the main ray grating method to improve the efficiency of the main ray generation and its experimental verification.', '20114914580699 (JA)', 0, 0, '1', '2011', '207-215', NULL, '', 2, 'He Jin, Fang Zhiyi, Ji Liang, Cai Ruicheng, Chen Lin', 't', '62', '0'),
(392, 'Design of an enhanced fuzzy k-nearest neighbor classifier based computer aided diagnostic system for thyroid disease', 'uploadFile/caa5466e-543a-4d33-8731-0c09937c862c.txt', '0', 18, 82, 49, '2012-12-13 16:10:04', '2013-10-29', '1', 'Journal of Medical Systems', '2012-09', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, 0, '4', '3', '11-18', NULL, '', 2, 'Da-You Liu, Hui-Ling Chen, Bo Yang, Xin-En Lv, Li-Na Li, Jie Liu', 't', '63', '0'),
(393, 'A Task Scheduling Algorithm for Multi-Core-Cluster Systems', 'uploadFile/398d18c4-ea70-4f6a-9d87-92785cbbb27e.pdf', 'no', 54, 54, 41, '2012-12-14 00:29:11', '2012-12-14', '1', 'Journal of Computers', '2012-11', 'Terms—task duplication, task scheduling, multi-core', 'no', 'Abstract—The quantity of cores on one chip increases\nrapidly with the development of multi-core technology,\nwhich has led to more complex structure of cluster system\nand greatly increasing number of tasks. In order to schedule\ntasks in multi-core-cluster systems efficiently, a task\nschedule model based on the directed acyclic graph(DAG) is\nbuilt, and then a algorithm based on task duplication is\nproposed. The algorithm is composed of two steps of\noperations, in which the processes are assigned to processor\nnodes in the first step and the threads in processes are\nassigned to core nodes in the second step respectively. The\ntime complexity of this algorithm is less than similar\nalgorithms. For the algorithm, minimization scheduling\nlength is the primary objective, and keeping load balancing\nbetween processing nodes is secondary objectives. It can be\nseen through comparison with correlative work that the\nalgorithm has advantages in scheduling length; furthermore,\nwhile the ratio of total communication cost and total\ncomputation cost in the task schedule model becomes larger,\nthe advantage of this algorithm is more obvious.', '20124815733669', 0, 0, '7', '11', '2797-2804', NULL, '', 2, 'Geng Xiaozhong,Xu Gaochao, Fu Xiaodong,Zhang Yuan.', 't', '62', 'no'),
(394, 'Multi-dimension and multi-level associated cache partitioning mechanism in CMP', 'uploadFile/0d24313f-e4f0-4bd0-b477-79f1acae555d.mht', 'no', 54, 54, 41, '2012-12-14 00:34:09', '2012-12-14', '1', 'International Journal of Advancements in Computing Technology', '2012-12', 'On the basis of a chip-multiprocessor with a shared cache structure', 'On the basis of a chip-multiprocessor with a shared cache structure, this paper proposes a new associated partitioning framework of multi-level Cache which is called UF-ACP (Utility and Fair-based Associated Cache Partitioning). The framework includes the associated structure of all the private L2 Caches and the partitioning algorithm of the last level Cache. Besides this paper designs application performance monitor (APM), which can dynamically collect hit and miss rate information of multiple multi-threaded applications on different cache partitions. The algorithm in this paper gives consideration to both utility and fair criterion, and the utility is based on miss rate. At the same time, the algorithm takes the process priority and the thread number into account. Because of all the reasons above mentioned, the algorithm improves throughput and fairness greatly. Experiments show that UFP improves throughput by up to 43.38% and 17.56% on average over the traditional non-partitioned shared cache with LRU replacement; and UFP improves the fairness by a factor of 3.8 on average over LRU and by a factor of 3.9 on average over Utility based Cache Partition (UCP).', '20122715194002\n', '20122715194002', 0, 0, '4', '10', '337-345', NULL, '', 2, 'Li Shuo,Xu Gaochao,Qiao Xiaolin3,Wu Feng.', 't', '63', 'no');
